870871,166,473,2,4,1,18,2,9 . Kāyagatāsatisuttaṃ 
870872,166,474,2,20,1,87,11,153. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
870873,166,474,21,33,1,139,11,Atha kho sambahulānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantānaṃ upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ ayamantarākathā udapādi–
870874,166,474,34,43,1,31,4,"‘‘ acchariyaṃ, āvuso, abbhutaṃ, āvuso! "
870875,166,474,44,72,1,129,14,Yāvañcidaṃ tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena kāyagatāsati[ kāyagatā sati( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā vuttā mahānisaṃsā’’ ti. 
870876,166,474,73,90,1,142,16,"Ayañca hidaṃ tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ antarākathā vippakatā hoti, atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena upaṭṭhānasālā tenupasaṅkami; "
870877,166,474,91,95,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
870878,166,474,96,101,1,36,5,Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
870879,166,474,102,122,1,87,13,"‘‘ kāya nuttha, bhikkhave, etarahi kathāya sannisinnā, kā ca pana vo antarākathā vippakatā’’ ti?"
870880,166,474,123,138,1,126,10,"‘‘ Idha , bhante, amhākaṃ pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantānaṃ upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ ayamantarākathā udapādi–"
870881,166,474,139,147,1,31,4,"‘ acchariyaṃ, āvuso, abbhutaṃ, āvuso! "
870882,166,474,148,163,1,129,14,Yāvañcidaṃ tena bhagavatā jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena kāyagatāsati bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā vuttā mahānisaṃsā’ ti. 
870883,166,474,164,179,1,66,10,"Ayaṃ kho no, bhante, antarākathā vippakatā, atha bhagavā anuppatto’’ ti. "
870884,166,475,2,21,1,86,10,"154.‘‘ Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, kāyagatāsati kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā? "
870885,166,475,22,42,1,151,18,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. "
870886,166,475,43,48,1,35,5,So satova assasati satova passasati; 
870887,166,475,49,68,1,97,14,"dīghaṃ vā assasanto‘ dīghaṃ assasāmī’ ti pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto‘ dīghaṃ passasāmī’ ti pajānāti; "
870888,166,475,69,88,1,97,14,"rassaṃ vā assasanto‘ rassaṃ assasāmī’ ti pajānāti, rassaṃ vā passasanto‘ rassaṃ passasāmī’ ti pajānāti;"
870889,166,475,89,102,1,90,8,"‘ sabbakāyapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ ti sikkhati,‘ sabbakāyapaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ ti sikkhati;"
870890,166,475,103,118,1,102,10,"‘ passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ ti sikkhati,‘ passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ ti sikkhati. "
870891,166,475,119,137,1,91,11,Tassa evaṃ appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato ye gehasitā[ gehassitā( ṭīkā)] sarasaṅkappā te pahīyanti . 
870892,166,475,138,163,1,79,9,"Tesaṃ pahānā ajjhattameva cittaṃ santiṭṭhati sannisīdati ekodi hoti[ ekodī hoti( sī.), ekodibhoti( syā. kaṃ.)] samādhiyati. "
870893,166,475,164,183,1,44,5,"Evaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāyagatāsatiṃ[ kāyagataṃ satiṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] bhāveti."
870894,166,476,2,42,1,160,25,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu gacchanto vā‘ gacchāmī’ ti pajānāti, ṭhito vā‘ ṭhitomhī’ ti pajānāti, nisinno vā‘ nisinnomhī’ ti pajānāti, sayāno vā‘ sayānomhī’ ti pajānāti. "
870895,166,476,43,55,1,66,11,"Yathā yathā vā panassa kāyo paṇihito hoti, tathā tathā naṃ pajānāti. "
870896,166,476,56,67,1,91,11,Tassa evaṃ appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato ye gehasitā sarasaṅkappā te pahīyanti. 
870897,166,476,68,78,1,79,9,Tesaṃ pahānā ajjhattameva cittaṃ santiṭṭhati sannisīdati ekodi hoti samādhiyati. 
870898,166,476,79,86,1,46,5,"Evampi, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāyagatāsatiṃ bhāveti."
