871174,166,530,1,4,1,12,1,3. Suññatavaggo
871175,166,531,2,4,1,17,2,1 . Cūḷasuññatasuttaṃ 
871176,166,532,2,21,1,82,10,176. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati pubbārāme migāramātupāsāde. 
871177,166,532,22,32,1,85,10,Atha kho āyasmā ānando sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
871178,166,532,33,38,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
871179,166,532,39,46,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
871180,166,532,47,61,1,79,10,"‘‘ ekamidaṃ, bhante, samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati nagarakaṃ nāma sakyānaṃ nigamo. "
871181,166,532,62,73,1,63,8,"Tattha me, bhante, bhagavato sammukhā sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ–"
871182,166,532,74,84,1,53,6,"‘ suññatāvihārenāhaṃ, ānanda, etarahi bahulaṃ viharāmī’ ti. "
871183,166,532,85,97,1,68,8,"Kacci metaṃ, bhante, sussutaṃ suggahitaṃ sumanasikataṃ sūpadhāritan’’ ti?"
871184,166,532,98,110,1,68,8,"‘‘ Taggha te etaṃ, ānanda, sussutaṃ suggahitaṃ sumanasikataṃ sūpadhāritaṃ. "
871185,166,532,111,139,1,60,6,"Pubbepāhaṃ[ pubbecāhaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)], ānanda, etarahipi[ etarahi ca( sabbattha)] suññatāvihārena bahulaṃ viharāmi. "
871186,166,532,140,162,1,182,17,"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, ayaṃ migāramātupāsādo suñño hatthigavassavaḷavena, suñño jātarūparajatena, suñño itthipurisasannipātena atthi cevidaṃ asuññataṃ yadidaṃ– bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṭicca ekattaṃ; "
871187,166,532,163,181,1,124,13,"evameva kho, ānanda, bhikkhu amanasikaritvā gāmasaññaṃ, amanasikaritvā manussasaññaṃ, araññasaññaṃ paṭicca manasi karoti ekattaṃ . "
871188,166,532,182,189,1,71,7,Tassa araññasaññāya cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati adhimuccati. 
871189,166,532,190,193,1,16,3,So evaṃ pajānāti–
871190,166,532,194,223,1,169,24,"‘ ye assu darathā gāmasaññaṃ paṭicca tedha na santi, ye assu darathā manussasaññaṃ paṭicca tedha na santi, atthi cevāyaṃ darathamattā yadidaṃ– araññasaññaṃ paṭicca ekattan’ ti. "
871191,166,532,224,252,1,161,19,"So‘ suññamidaṃ saññāgataṃ gāmasaññāyā’ ti pajānāti,‘ suññamidaṃ saññāgataṃ manussasaññāyā’ ti pajānāti,‘ atthi cevidaṃ asuññataṃ yadidaṃ– araññasaññaṃ paṭicca ekattan’ ti. "
871192,166,532,253,280,1,123,20,"Iti yañhi kho tattha na hoti tena taṃ suññaṃ samanupassati, yaṃ pana tattha avasiṭṭhaṃ hoti taṃ‘ santamidaṃ atthī’’’ ti pajānāti. "
871193,166,532,281,291,1,80,8,"Evampissa esā, ānanda, yathābhuccā avipallatthā parisuddhā suññatāvakkanti bhavati. "
871194,166,533,2,25,1,128,13,"177.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhu amanasikaritvā manussasaññaṃ, amanasikaritvā araññasaññaṃ, pathavīsaññaṃ paṭicca manasi karoti ekattaṃ. "
871195,166,533,26,34,1,72,7,Tassa pathavīsaññāya cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati adhimuccati. 
871196,166,533,35,43,1,66,6,"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, āsabhacammaṃ saṅkusatena suvihataṃ vigatavalikaṃ; "
871197,166,533,44,72,1,180,19,"evameva kho, ānanda, bhikkhu yaṃ imissā pathaviyā ukkūlavikkūlaṃ nadīviduggaṃ khāṇukaṇṭakaṭṭhānaṃ pabbatavisamaṃ taṃ sabbaṃ[ sabbaṃ( ka.)] amanasikaritvā pathavīsaññaṃ paṭicca manasi karoti ekattaṃ. "
871198,166,533,73,80,1,72,7,Tassa pathavīsaññāya cittaṃ pakkhandati pasīdati santiṭṭhati adhimuccati. 
871199,166,533,81,84,1,16,3,So evaṃ pajānāti–
871200,166,533,85,115,1,172,24,"‘ ye assu darathā manussasaññaṃ paṭicca tedha na santi, ye assu darathā araññasaññaṃ paṭicca tedha na santi, atthi cevāyaṃ darathamattā yadidaṃ– pathavīsaññaṃ paṭicca ekattan’ ti. "
871201,166,533,116,144,1,164,19,"So‘ suññamidaṃ saññāgataṃ manussasaññāyā’ ti pajānāti,‘ suññamidaṃ saññāgataṃ araññasaññāyā’ ti pajānāti,‘ atthi cevidaṃ asuññataṃ yadidaṃ– pathavīsaññaṃ paṭicca ekattan’ ti. "
871202,166,533,145,168,1,123,20,"Iti yañhi kho tattha na hoti tena taṃ suññaṃ samanupassati, yaṃ pana tattha avasiṭṭhaṃ hoti taṃ‘ santamidaṃ atthī’ ti pajānāti. "
871203,166,533,169,179,1,80,8,"Evampissa esā, ānanda, yathābhuccā avipallatthā parisuddhā suññatāvakkanti bhavati. "
871204,166,534,2,25,1,137,13,"178.‘‘ Puna caparaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhu amanasikaritvā araññasaññaṃ, amanasikaritvā pathavīsaññaṃ, ākāsānañcāyatanasaññaṃ paṭicca manasi karoti ekattaṃ. "
