871255,166,540,105,143,1,112,13,"Tasmātiha, ānanda,‘ parisuddhaṃ paramānuttaraṃ suññataṃ upasampajja viharissāmā’ ti[ viharissāmīti( pī. ka.)]– evañhi vo[ te( ka.)], ānanda, sikkhitabban’’ ti. "
871256,166,541,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
871257,166,541,5,11,1,53,6,Attamano āyasmā ānando bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. 
