871259,166,543,2,4,1,17,2,2 . Mahāsuññatasuttaṃ 
871260,166,544,2,19,1,81,10,185. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ nigrodhārāme. 
871261,166,544,20,29,1,89,9,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kapilavatthuṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
871262,166,544,30,41,1,129,11,Kapilavatthusmiṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena kāḷakhemakassa sakkassa vihāro tenupasaṅkami divāvihārāya. 
871263,166,544,42,54,1,93,11,Tena kho pana samayena kāḷakhemakassa sakkassa vihāre sambahulāni senāsanāni paññattāni honti. 
871264,166,544,55,65,1,83,9,Addasā kho bhagavā kāḷakhemakassa sakkassa vihāre sambahulāni senāsanāni paññattāni. 
871265,166,544,66,69,1,27,3,Disvāna bhagavato etadahosi–
871266,166,544,70,79,1,68,7,‘‘ sambahulāni kho kāḷakhemakassa sakkassa vihāre senāsanāni paññattāni. 
871267,166,544,80,89,1,42,7,Sambahulā nu kho idha bhikkhū viharantī’’ ti. 
871268,166,545,2,20,1,110,14,186. Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā ānando sambahulehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ ghaṭāya sakkassa vihāre cīvarakammaṃ karoti. 
871269,166,545,21,32,1,95,11,Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yena ghaṭāya sakkassa vihāro tenupasaṅkami; 
871270,166,545,33,37,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
871271,166,545,38,44,1,47,6,Nisajja kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi–
871272,166,545,45,58,1,75,8,"‘‘ sambahulāni kho, ānanda, kāḷakhemakassa sakkassa vihāre senāsanāni paññattāni. "
871273,166,545,59,68,1,43,7,Sambahulā nu kho ettha bhikkhū viharantī’’ ti?
871274,166,545,69,80,1,71,7,"‘‘ Sambahulāni, bhante, kāḷakhemakassa sakkassa vihāre senāsanāni paññattāni. "
871275,166,545,81,85,1,33,4,Sambahulā bhikkhū ettha viharanti. 
871276,166,545,86,95,1,37,5,"Cīvarakārasamayo no, bhante, vattatī’’ ti."
871277,166,546,2,18,1,115,13,"‘ ‘ Na kho, ānanda, bhikkhu sobhati saṅgaṇikārāmo saṅgaṇikarato saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ anuyutto gaṇārāmo gaṇarato gaṇasammudito. "
871278,166,546,19,67,1,261,25,"So vatānanda, bhikkhu saṅgaṇikārāmo saṅgaṇikarato saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ anuyutto gaṇārāmo gaṇarato gaṇasammudito yaṃ taṃ nekkhammasukhaṃ pavivekasukhaṃ upasamasukhaṃ sambodhisukhaṃ[ sambodhasukhaṃ( sī. pī.), sambodhasukhaṃ cittekaggatāsukhaṃ( ka.) upari araṇavibhaṅgasutte pana sambodhisukhantveva dissati] tassa sukhassa nikāmalābhī bhavissati akicchalābhī akasiralābhīti– netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
871279,166,546,68,99,1,243,27,"Yo ca kho so, ānanda, bhikkhu eko gaṇasmā vūpakaṭṭho viharati tassetaṃ bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ yaṃ taṃ nekkhammasukhaṃ pavivekasukhaṃ upasamasukhaṃ sambodhisukhaṃ tassa sukhassa nikāmalābhī bhavissati akicchalābhī akasiralābhīti– ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
871280,166,547,2,28,1,208,23,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu saṅgaṇikārāmo saṅgaṇikarato saṅgaṇikārāmataṃ anuyutto gaṇārāmo gaṇarato gaṇasammudito sāmāyikaṃ vā kantaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharissati asāmāyikaṃ vā akuppanti– netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
871281,166,547,29,58,1,190,24,"Yo ca kho so, ānanda, bhikkhu eko gaṇasmā vūpakaṭṭho viharati tassetaṃ bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ sāmāyikaṃ vā kantaṃ cetovimuttiṃ upasampajja viharissati asāmāyikaṃ vā akuppanti– ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
871282,166,548,2,26,1,150,14,"‘ ‘ Nāhaṃ, ānanda, ekaṃ rūpampi[ ekarūpampi( sī.)] samanupassāmi yattha rattassa yathābhiratassa rūpassa vipariṇāmaññathābhāvā na uppajjeyyuṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassūpāyāsā. "
871283,166,549,2,43,1,128,13,"187.‘‘ Ayaṃ kho panānanda, vihāro tathāgatena abhisambuddho yadidaṃ– sabbanimittānaṃ amanasikārā ajjhattaṃ suññataṃ upasampajja viharituṃ[ viharataṃ( ka. sī.), viharati( syā. kaṃ. ka.)]. "
871284,166,549,44,76,1,159,17,"Tatra ce, ānanda, tathāgataṃ iminā vihārena viharantaṃ bhavanti[ bhagavantaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. ka.)] upasaṅkamitāro bhikkhū bhikkhuniyo upāsakā upāsikāyo rājāno rājamahāmattā titthiyā titthiyasāvakā. "
871285,166,549,77,95,1,210,17,"Tatrānanda, tathāgato vivekaninneneva cittena vivekapoṇena vivekapabbhārena vūpakaṭṭhena nekkhammābhiratena byantībhūtena sabbaso āsavaṭṭhānīyehi dhammehi aññadatthu uyyojanikapaṭisaṃyuttaṃyeva kathaṃ kattā hoti. "
