871287,166,549,102,120,1,145,14,"‘ ajjhattaṃ suññataṃ upasampajja vihareyyan’ ti, tenānanda, bhikkhunā ajjhattameva cittaṃ saṇṭhapetabbaṃ sannisādetabbaṃ ekodi kātabbaṃ samādahātabbaṃ. "
871288,166,550,2,31,1,89,9,"188.‘‘ Kathañcānanda, bhikkhu ajjhattameva cittaṃ saṇṭhapeti sannisādeti ekodiṃ karoti[ ekodikaroti( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] samādahati? "
871289,166,550,32,60,1,172,21,"Idhānanda, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi… pe… paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati… pe… dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ… tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ… catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
