871527,166,595,2,4,1,12,2,4 . Bākulasuttaṃ 
871528,166,596,2,33,1,83,11,209. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā bākulo[ bakkulo( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
871529,166,596,34,45,1,88,9,Atha kho acelakassapo āyasmato bākulassa purāṇagihisahāyo yenāyasmā bākulo tenupasaṅkami; 
871530,166,596,46,51,1,47,5,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā bākulena saddhiṃ sammodi. 
871531,166,596,52,58,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
871532,166,596,59,66,1,63,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho acelakassapo āyasmantaṃ bākulaṃ etadavoca–
871533,166,597,2,12,1,37,6,"‘ ‘ Kīvaciraṃ pabbajitosi, āvuso bākulā’’ ti?"
871534,166,597,13,25,1,38,6,"‘‘ Asīti me, āvuso, vassāni pabbajitassā’’ ti."
871535,166,597,26,44,1,84,12,"‘‘ Imehi pana te, āvuso bākula, asītiyā vassehi katikkhattuṃ methuno dhammo paṭisevito’’ ti?"
871536,166,597,45,56,1,42,7,"‘‘ Na kho maṃ, āvuso kassapa, evaṃ pucchitabbaṃ–"
871537,166,597,57,73,1,84,12,"‘ imehi pana te, āvuso bākula, asītiyā vassehi katikkhattuṃ methuno dhammo paṭisevito’ ti. "
871538,166,597,74,82,1,41,6,"Evañca kho maṃ, āvuso kassapa, pucchitabbaṃ–"
871539,166,597,83,123,1,81,11,"‘ imehi pana te, āvuso bākula, asītiyā vassehi katikkhattuṃ kāmasaññā uppannapubbā’’’ ti?()[( imehi pana te āvuso bakkula asītiyo vassehi katikkhattuṃ kāmasaññā uppannapubbāti.)( sī. pī.)] "
871540,166,598,2,19,1,72,8,"210.‘‘ Asīti me, āvuso , vassāni pabbajitassa nābhijānāmi kāmasaññaṃ uppannapubbaṃ. "
871541,166,598,20,34,1,136,14,Yaṃpāyasmā bākulo asītiyā vassehi nābhijānāti kāmasaññaṃ uppannapubbaṃ idampi mayaṃ āyasmato bākulassa acchariyaṃ abbhutadhammaṃ dhārema.
871542,166,599,2,18,1,92,11,"‘ ‘ Asīti me, āvuso, vassāni pabbajitassa nābhijānāmi byāpādasaññaṃ… pe… vihiṃsāsaññaṃ uppannapubbaṃ. "
871543,166,599,19,34,1,139,14,"Yaṃpāyasmā bākulo asītiyā vassehi nābhijānāti vihiṃsāsaññaṃ uppannapubbaṃ, idampi mayaṃ āyasmato bākulassa acchariyaṃ abbhutadhammaṃ dhārema."
