871586,166,613,44,55,1,72,9,‘ Sādhu me bhavaṃ aggivessano yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ desetū’ ti.
871587,166,613,56,69,1,76,10,"‘ Na kho te ahaṃ, rājakumāra, sakkomi yathāsutaṃ yathāpariyattaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ. "
