871644,166,622,113,135,1,39,6,"‘ abbhokāsagato kho[ kho te( syā. kaṃ. ka.)], deva, āraññako nāgo’ ti. "
871645,166,622,136,146,1,79,9,"Atha kho aggivessana, tamenaṃ rājā khattiyo muddhāvasitto hatthidamakaṃ āmantesi–"
871646,166,622,147,181,1,261,22,"‘ ehi tvaṃ, samma hatthidamaka, āraññakaṃ nāgaṃ damayāhi āraññakānañceva sīlānaṃ abhinimmadanāya āraññakānañceva sarasaṅkappānaṃ abhinimmadanāya āraññakānañceva darathakilamathapariḷāhānaṃ abhinimmadanāya gāmante abhiramāpanāya manussakantesu sīlesu samādapanāyā’’’ ti[ samādāpanāyāti(?)]."
871647,166,623,2,43,1,375,33,"‘ ‘‘ Evaṃ , devā’ ti kho, aggivessana, hatthidamako rañño khattiyassa muddhāvasittassa paṭissutvā mahantaṃ thambhaṃ pathaviyaṃ nikhaṇitvā āraññakassa nāgassa gīvāyaṃ upanibandhati āraññakānañceva sīlānaṃ abhinimmadanāya āraññakānañceva sarasaṅkappānaṃ abhinimmadanāya āraññakānañceva darathakilamathapariḷāhānaṃ abhinimmadanāya gāmante abhiramāpanāya manussakantesu sīlesu samādapanāya. "
871648,166,623,44,59,1,134,15,Tamenaṃ hatthidamako yā sā vācā nelā kaṇṇasukhā pemanīyā hadayaṅgamā porī bahujanakantā bahujanamanāpā tathārūpāhi vācāhi samudācarati. 
871649,166,623,60,90,1,216,25,"Yato kho, aggivessana, āraññako nāgo hatthidamakassa yā sā vācā nelā kaṇṇasukhā pemanīyā hadayaṅgamā porī bahujanakantā bahujanamanāpā tathārūpāhi vācāhi samudācariyamāno sussūsati, sotaṃ odahati, aññā cittaṃ upaṭṭhāpeti; "
871650,166,623,91,96,1,57,5,tamenaṃ hatthidamako uttari tiṇaghāsodakaṃ anuppavecchati.
871651,166,624,2,20,1,110,13,"‘ ‘ Yato kho, aggivessana, āraññako nāgo hatthidamakassa tiṇaghāsodakaṃ paṭiggaṇhāti, tatra hatthidamakassa evaṃ hoti–"
871652,166,624,21,48,1,35,6,‘ jīvissati kho[ nu kho( sī. ka.)] dāni āraññako[ rañño( sī. pī.)] nāgo’ ti. 
871653,166,624,49,54,1,42,5,Tamenaṃ hatthidamako uttari kāraṇaṃ kāreti–
871654,166,624,55,65,1,25,5,"‘ ādiya, bho, nikkhipa, bho’ ti. "
871655,166,624,66,84,1,138,15,"Yato kho, aggivessana, āraññako nāgo hatthidamakassa ādānanikkhepe vacanakaro hoti ovādappaṭikaro, tamenaṃ hatthidamako uttari kāraṇaṃ kāreti–"
871656,166,624,85,95,1,30,5,"‘ abhikkama, bho, paṭikkama, bho’ ti. "
871657,166,624,96,113,1,142,14,"Yato kho, aggivessana, āraññako nāgo hatthidamakassa abhikkamapaṭikkamavacanakaro hoti ovādappaṭikaro, tamenaṃ hatthidamako uttari kāraṇaṃ kāreti–"
871658,166,624,114,124,1,25,5,"‘ uṭṭhaha, bho, nisīda, bho’ ti. "
871659,166,624,125,174,1,362,41,"Yato kho, aggivessana, āraññako nāgo hatthidamakassa uṭṭhānanisajjāya vacanakaro hoti ovādappaṭikaro, tamenaṃ hatthidamako uttari āneñjaṃ nāma kāraṇaṃ kāreti, mahantassa phalakaṃ soṇḍāya upanibandhati, tomarahattho ca puriso uparigīvāya nisinno hoti, samantato ca tomarahatthā purisā parivāretvā ṭhitā honti, hatthidamako ca dīghatomarayaṭṭhiṃ gahetvā purato ṭhito hoti. "
871660,166,624,175,215,1,209,33,"So āneñjaṃ kāraṇaṃ kāriyamāno neva purime pāde copeti na pacchime pāde copeti, na purimakāyaṃ copeti na pacchimakāyaṃ copeti, na sīsaṃ copeti, na kaṇṇe copeti, na dante copeti , na naṅguṭṭhaṃ copeti, na soṇḍaṃ copeti. "
871661,166,624,216,257,1,223,17,"So hoti āraññako nāgo khamo sattippahārānaṃ asippahārānaṃ usuppahārānaṃ sarapattappahārānaṃ[ parasatthappahārānaṃ( sī.), parasattuppahārānaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] bheripaṇavavaṃsasaṅkhaḍiṇḍimaninnādasaddānaṃ[ bheripaṇavasaṅkhatiṇavaninnādasaddānaṃ( pī.)] sabbavaṅkadosanihitaninnītakasāvo rājāraho rājabhoggo rañño aṅganteva saṅkhaṃ gacchati. "
871662,166,625,2,29,1,176,18,"218.‘‘ Evameva kho, aggivessana, idha tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā. "
871663,166,625,30,43,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
871664,166,625,44,57,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
871665,166,625,58,70,1,78,11,Taṃ dhammaṃ suṇāti gahapati vā gahapatiputto vā aññatarasmiṃ vā kule paccājāto. 
871666,166,625,71,78,1,50,7,So taṃ dhammaṃ sutvā tathāgate saddhaṃ paṭilabhati. 
871667,166,625,79,85,1,57,6,So tena saddhāpaṭilābhena samannāgato iti paṭisañcikkhati–
871668,166,625,86,93,1,47,5,"‘ sambādho gharāvāso rajāpatho, abbhokāso pabbajjā. "
