871689,166,631,26,48,1,163,19,"So dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate… pe… yathākammūpage satte pajānāti."
