871691,166,632,21,54,1,184,22,"So‘ idaṃ dukkhan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti;"
871692,166,632,55,87,1,175,21,"‘ ime āsavā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ āsavasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
