871964,166,670,46,68,1,112,14,"‘‘ Tadaṅgena kho, āvuso kaccāna, santettha ekaccā devatā saṃkiliṭṭhābhā, santi panettha ekaccā devatā parisuddhābhā’’ ti."
871965,166,670,69,102,1,177,24,"‘‘ Ko nu kho, bhante, anuruddha, hetu ko paccayo, yena tāsaṃ devatānaṃ ekaṃ devanikāyaṃ upapannānaṃ santettha ekaccā devatā saṃkiliṭṭhābhā, santi panettha ekaccā devatā parisuddhābhā’’ ti?"
871966,166,671,2,13,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Tena , hāvuso kaccāna, upamaṃ te karissāmi. "
871967,166,671,14,27,1,57,6,Upamāyapidhekacce[ upamāyamidhekacce( ka.)] viññū purisā bhāsitassa atthaṃ ājānanti. 
871968,166,671,28,39,1,88,9,"Seyyathāpi, āvuso kaccāna, telappadīpassa jhāyato telampi aparisuddhaṃ vaṭṭipi aparisuddhā. "
871969,166,671,40,48,1,76,8,So telassapi aparisuddhattā vaṭṭiyāpi aparisuddhattā andhandhaṃ viya jhāyati; 
871970,166,671,49,81,1,220,24,"evameva kho, āvuso kaccāna, idhekacco bhikkhu‘ saṃkiliṭṭhābhā’ ti pharitvā adhimuccitvā viharati, tassa kāyaduṭṭhullampi na suppaṭippassaddhaṃ hoti, thinamiddhampi na susamūhataṃ hoti , uddhaccakukkuccampi na suppaṭivinītaṃ hoti. "
871971,166,671,82,95,1,145,13,So kāyaduṭṭhullassapi na suppaṭippassaddhattā thinamiddhassapi na susamūhatattā uddhaccakukkuccassapi na suppaṭivinītattā andhandhaṃ viya jhāyati. 
