872640,166,809,53,57,1,26,4,So tena dvārena nikkhamati. 
872641,166,810,2,20,1,81,9,"269.‘‘ Tassa kho pana, bhikkhave, mahānirayassa samanantarā sahitameva mahanto gūthanirayo. "
872642,166,810,21,24,1,16,3,So tattha patati. 
872643,166,810,25,61,1,228,29,"Tasmiṃ kho pana, bhikkhave, gūthaniraye sūcimukhā pāṇā chaviṃ chindanti, chaviṃ chetvā cammaṃ chindanti, cammaṃ chetvā maṃsaṃ chindanti, maṃsaṃ chetvā nhāruṃ chindanti, nhāruṃ chetvā aṭṭhiṃ chindanti, aṭṭhiṃ chetvā aṭṭhimiñjaṃ khādanti. "
