872699,166,834,2,4,1,19,2,1 . Bhaddekarattasuttaṃ 
872700,166,835,2,21,1,87,11,272. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
872701,166,835,22,27,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
872702,166,835,28,34,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
872703,166,835,35,45,1,44,6,‘‘ Bhadante’’ ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. 
872704,166,835,46,48,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
872705,166,835,49,59,1,61,6,"‘‘ bhaddekarattassa vo, bhikkhave, uddesañca vibhaṅgañca desessāmi. "
872706,166,835,60,66,1,35,5,"Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha; "
872707,166,835,67,71,1,13,2,bhāsissāmī’’ ti.
872708,166,835,72,85,1,51,8,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
872709,166,835,86,88,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
872710,166,836,2,9,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya, nappaṭikaṅkhe anāgataṃ; "
872711,166,837,2,8,1,41,5,"Yadatītaṃ pahīnaṃ taṃ, appattañca anāgataṃ."
872712,166,838,2,17,1,49,7,"‘ ‘ Paccuppannañca yo[ yaṃ( nettipāḷi)] dhammaṃ, tattha tattha vipassati; "
872713,166,839,2,19,1,42,5,"Asaṃhīraṃ [ asaṃhiraṃ( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] asaṃkuppaṃ, taṃ vidvā manubrūhaye."
872714,166,840,2,21,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Ajjeva kiccamātappaṃ[ kiccaṃ ātappaṃ( sī. ka.)], ko jaññā maraṇaṃ suve; "
872715,166,841,2,10,1,41,7,"Na hi no saṅgaraṃ tena, mahāsenena maccunā."
872716,166,842,2,9,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ vihāriṃ ātāpiṃ, ahorattamatanditaṃ; "
872717,166,843,2,24,1,43,6,"Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti, santo ācikkhate muni’’[ munīti( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)]. "
872718,166,844,2,16,1,36,4,"273.‘‘ Kathañca , bhikkhave, atītaṃ anvāgameti?"
872719,166,844,17,75,1,346,40,"‘ Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti,‘ evaṃvedano ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti,‘ evaṃsañño ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti,‘ evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti,‘ evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti– evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atītaṃ anvāgameti."
872720,166,845,2,10,1,37,5,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, atītaṃ nānvāgameti?"
872721,166,845,11,74,1,362,45,"‘ Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti,‘ evaṃvedano ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti,‘ evaṃsañño ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti,‘ evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti,‘ evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti– evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, atītaṃ nānvāgameti. "
872722,166,846,2,14,1,40,4,"274.‘‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati?"
872723,166,846,15,50,1,219,25,"‘ Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano siyaṃ… pe… evaṃsañño siyaṃ… evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ… evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti– evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati."
872724,166,847,2,10,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati?"
872725,166,847,11,50,1,226,27,"‘ Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃvedano siyaṃ … evaṃsañño siyaṃ… evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ…‘ evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānan’ ti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti– evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati. "
872726,166,848,2,15,1,51,5,"275.‘‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati? "
872727,166,848,16,49,1,253,28,"Idha, bhikkhave, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ; "
872728,166,848,50,82,1,175,22,"vedanaṃ… pe… saññaṃ… saṅkhāre… viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ attani vā viññāṇaṃ, viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ– evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati."
872729,166,849,2,13,1,54,7,"‘ ‘ Kathañca , bhikkhave, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati? "
872730,166,849,14,51,1,262,32,"Idha, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako ariyānaṃ dassāvī ariyadhammassa kovido ariyadhamme suvinīto sappurisānaṃ dassāvī sappurisadhammassa kovido sappurisadhamme suvinīto na rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā rūpaṃ, na rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ; "
872731,166,849,52,90,1,196,29,"na vedanaṃ… na saññaṃ… na saṅkhāre… na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, na viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā viññāṇaṃ, na viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ– evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati."
