872753,166,864,9,34,1,153,17,"‘‘ yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi , bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī’’ ti?"
872754,166,864,35,55,1,146,15,"‘‘ Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsiṃ–"
