872892,166,926,72,77,1,29,3,Vibhajatāyasmā mahākaccāno’’ ti.
872893,166,927,2,27,1,184,20,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, āvuso, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva mūlaṃ atikkamma khandhaṃ sākhāpalāse sāraṃ pariyesitabbaṃ maññeyya; "
872894,166,927,28,47,1,120,12,evaṃ sampadamidaṃ āyasmantānaṃ satthari sammukhībhūte taṃ bhagavantaṃ atisitvā amhe etamatthaṃ paṭipucchitabbaṃ maññatha[ maññetha( pī.)]. 
872895,166,927,48,70,1,158,19,"So hāvuso, bhagavā jānaṃ jānāti, passaṃ passati, cakkhubhūto ñāṇabhūto dhammabhūto brahmabhūto vattā pavattā atthassa ninnetā amatassa dātā dhammassāmī tathāgato. "
872896,166,927,71,91,1,129,17,"So ceva panetassa kālo ahosi yaṃ bhagavantaṃyeva etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyātha, yathā vo bhagavā byākareyya tathā naṃ dhāreyyāthā’’ ti."
872897,166,928,2,26,1,166,20,"‘ ‘ Addhāvuso kaccāna, bhagavā jānaṃ jānāti, passaṃ passati, cakkhubhūto ñāṇabhūto dhammabhūto brahmabhūto vattā pavattā atthassa ninnetā amatassa dātā dhammassāmī tathāgato. "
872898,166,928,27,36,1,75,9,So ceva panetassa kālo ahosi yaṃ bhagavantaṃyeva etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyāma; 
872899,166,928,37,44,1,48,7,yathā no bhagavā byākareyya tathā naṃ dhāreyyāma. 
872900,166,928,45,54,1,84,9,Api cāyasmā mahākaccāno satthuceva saṃvaṇṇito sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ; 
