872915,166,935,12,37,1,187,21,"Iti me cakkhu ahosi atītamaddhānaṃ iti rūpāti– tattha na chandarāgappaṭibaddhaṃ hoti viññāṇaṃ, na chandarāgappaṭibaddhattā viññāṇassa na tadabhinandati, na tadabhinandanto atītaṃ nānvāgameti. "
