873189,166,1018,2,4,1,23,2,6 . Mahākammavibhaṅgasuttaṃ 
873190,166,1019,2,20,1,77,10,298. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
873191,166,1019,21,30,1,63,8,Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā samiddhi araññakuṭikāyaṃ viharati. 
873192,166,1019,31,41,1,108,10,Atha kho potaliputto paribbājako jaṅghāvihāraṃ anucaṅkamamāno anuvicaramāno yenāyasmā samiddhi tenupasaṅkami; 
873193,166,1019,42,47,1,49,5,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā samiddhinā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
873194,166,1019,48,54,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
873195,166,1019,55,63,1,76,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho potaliputto paribbājako āyasmantaṃ samiddhiṃ etadavoca–
873196,166,1019,64,78,1,77,9,"‘‘ sammukhā metaṃ, āvuso samiddhi, samaṇassa gotamassa sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ–"
873197,166,1019,79,89,1,59,7,"‘ moghaṃ kāyakammaṃ moghaṃ vacīkammaṃ, manokammameva saccan’ ti. "
873198,166,1019,90,113,1,67,11,Atthi ca sā[ atthi cesā( sī. ka.)] samāpatti yaṃ samāpattiṃ samāpanno na kiñci vediyatī’’ ti?
873199,166,1019,114,147,1,59,8,"‘‘ Mā hevaṃ, āvuso potaliputta, avaca;( mā hevaṃ, āvuso potaliputta, avaca;)[() syā. kaṃ. potthakesu natthi] mā bhagavantaṃ abbhācikkhi. "
873200,166,1019,148,153,1,34,5,Na hi sādhu bhagavato abbhakkhānaṃ. 
873201,166,1019,154,159,1,26,5,Na hi bhagavā evaṃ vadeyya–
873202,166,1019,160,170,1,59,7,"‘ moghaṃ kāyakammaṃ moghaṃ vacīkammaṃ, manokammameva saccan’ ti. "
