873207,166,1019,224,250,1,112,15,"‘‘ Ettha dāni mayaṃ there bhikkhū kiṃ vakkhāma, yatra hi nāma evaṃnavo bhikkhu[ navakena bhikkhunā( ka.)] satthāraṃ parirakkhitabbaṃ maññissati. "
873208,166,1019,251,268,1,80,12,"Sañcetanikaṃ, āvuso samiddhi, kammaṃ katvā kāyena vācāya manasā kiṃ so vediyatī’’ ti?"
873209,166,1019,269,287,1,87,12,"‘‘ Sañcetanikaṃ, āvuso potaliputta, kammaṃ katvā kāyena vācāya manasā dukkhaṃ so vediyatī’’ ti. "
873210,166,1019,288,298,1,90,10,Atha kho potaliputto paribbājako āyasmato samiddhissa bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandi nappaṭikkosi; 
873211,166,1019,299,303,1,49,4,anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. 
873212,166,1020,2,16,1,93,10,299. Atha kho āyasmā samiddhi acirapakkante potaliputte paribbājake yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkami; 
