873230,166,1023,2,22,1,44,6,300. Atha kho[ evaṃ vutte( syā. kaṃ.)] bhagavā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi–
873231,166,1023,23,54,1,62,8,"‘‘ passasi no tvaṃ, ānanda, imassa udāyissa moghapurisassa ummaṅgaṃ[ ummaggaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.), umaṅgaṃ( ka.)]? "
