873559,166,1080,16,53,1,206,16,"Idhāvuso, bhikkhuno cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā rūpanimittānusāri viññāṇaṃ hoti rūpanimittassādagadhitaṃ[… gathitaṃ( sī. pī.)] rūpanimittassādavinibandhaṃ[… vinibandhaṃ( sī. pī.)] rūpanimittassādasaṃyojanasaṃyuttaṃ bahiddhā viññāṇaṃ vikkhittaṃ visaṭanti vuccati. "
