873588,166,1090,2,13,1,37,4,"320.‘‘ Kathañcāvuso, anupādā paritassanā hoti? "
873589,166,1090,14,43,1,247,27,"Idhāvuso, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto rūpaṃ attato samanupassati rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ attani vā rūpaṃ rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ. "
873590,166,1090,44,51,1,41,6,"Tassa taṃ rūpaṃ vipariṇamati, aññathā hoti. "
