873613,166,1092,22,44,1,162,18,"‘ tathā tathā, bhikkhave, bhikkhu upaparikkheyya yathā yathā upaparikkhato bahiddhā cassa viññāṇaṃ avikkhittaṃ avisaṭaṃ, ajjhattaṃ asaṇṭhitaṃ anupādāya na paritasseyya. "
873614,166,1092,45,63,1,148,15,"Bahiddhā, bhikkhave, viññāṇe avikkhitte avisaṭe sati ajjhattaṃ asaṇṭhite anupādāya aparitassato āyatiṃ jātijarāmaraṇadukkhasamudayasambhavo na hotī’ ti. "
873615,166,1092,64,82,1,127,15,"Imassa kho ahaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmi. "
873616,166,1092,83,92,1,93,9,Ākaṅkhamānā ca pana tumhe āyasmanto bhagavantaṃyeva upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyātha; 
873617,166,1092,93,103,1,51,8,yathā vo bhagavā byākaroti tathā naṃ dhāreyyāthā’’ ti. 
873618,166,1093,2,19,1,118,13,322. Atha kho te bhikkhū āyasmato mahākaccānassa bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
873619,166,1093,20,26,1,57,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
873620,166,1093,27,34,1,55,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ–
873621,166,1094,2,21,1,114,15,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ kho no, bhante, bhagavā saṃkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho–"
873622,166,1094,22,44,1,162,18,"‘ tathā tathā, bhikkhave, bhikkhu upaparikkheyya yathā yathā upaparikkhato bahiddhā cassa viññāṇaṃ avikkhittaṃ avisaṭaṃ, ajjhattaṃ asaṇṭhitaṃ anupādāya na paritasseyya. "
873623,166,1094,45,65,1,148,15,"Bahiddhā, bhikkhave, viññāṇe avikkhitte avisaṭe sati ajjhattaṃ asaṇṭhite anupādāya aparitassato āyatiṃ jātijarāmaraṇadukkhasamudayasambhavo na hotī’’’ ti."
873624,166,1095,2,15,1,60,8,"‘ ‘ Tesaṃ no, bhante, amhākaṃ, acirapakkantassa bhagavato, etadahosi–"
873625,166,1095,16,56,1,277,32,"‘ idaṃ kho no, āvuso, bhagavā saṃkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho– tathā tathā, bhikkhave, bhikkhu upaparikkheyya, yathā yathā upaparikkhato bahiddhā cassa viññāṇaṃ avikkhittaṃ avisaṭaṃ, ajjhattaṃ asaṇṭhitaṃ anupādāya na paritasseyya. "
873626,166,1095,57,73,1,147,14,"Bahiddhā, bhikkhave, viññāṇe avikkhitte avisaṭe sati ajjhattaṃ asaṇṭhite anupādāya aparitassato āyatiṃ jātijarāmaraṇadukkhasamudayasambhavo na hotīti. "
873627,166,1095,74,90,1,123,15,Ko nu kho imassa bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajeyyā’ ti? 
873628,166,1095,91,98,1,33,5,"Tesaṃ no, bhante, amhākaṃ etadahosi–"
873629,166,1095,99,112,1,89,11,‘ ayaṃ kho āyasmā mahākaccāno satthu ceva saṃvaṇṇito sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ. 
