873655,166,1102,19,58,1,158,17,"Ete kho, bhikkhave[ ete kho( sī.), ete te( syā. kaṃ. pī.)], ubho ante anupagamma majjhimā paṭipadā tathāgatena abhisambuddhā, cakkhukaraṇī ñāṇakaraṇī upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattati. "
