873899,166,1148,21,28,1,38,5,"Katamā ca, bhikkhu, ajjhattikā tejodhātu? "
873900,166,1148,29,75,1,284,36,"Yaṃ ajjhattaṃ paccattaṃ tejo tejogataṃ upādinnaṃ, seyyathidaṃ– yena ca santappati, yena ca jīrīyati, yena ca pariḍayhati, yena ca asitapītakhāyitasāyitaṃ sammā pariṇāmaṃ gacchati, yaṃ vā panaññampi kiñci ajjhattaṃ paccattaṃ tejo tejogataṃ upādinnaṃ– ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, ajjhattikā tejodhātu. "
873901,166,1148,76,87,1,76,11,Yā ceva kho pana ajjhattikā tejodhātu yā ca bāhirā tejodhātu tejodhāturevesā.
873902,166,1148,88,105,1,88,12,"‘ Taṃ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti– evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
873903,166,1148,106,116,1,91,9,"Evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā tejodhātuyā nibbindati, tejodhātuyā cittaṃ virājeti. "
