874002,166,1168,2,12,1,25,4,370. Atha kho āyasmā pukkusāti–
874003,166,1168,13,41,1,175,23,"‘‘ satthā kira me anuppatto, sugato kira me anuppatto sammāsambuddho kira me anuppatto’’ ti uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ cīvaraṃ katvā bhagavato pādesu sirasā nipatitvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
