874248,166,1248,2,4,1,23,2,1 . Anāthapiṇḍikovādasuttaṃ 
874249,166,1249,2,22,1,87,11,383. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
874250,166,1249,23,33,1,80,10,Tena kho pana samayena anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. 
874251,166,1249,34,41,1,58,7,Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi–
874252,166,1249,42,53,1,48,7,"‘‘ ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkama; "
874253,166,1249,54,72,1,57,7,upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vandāhi[ vandāhi evañca vadehi( sabbattha) aññasuttesu pana natthi]–
874254,166,1249,73,82,1,59,6,"‘ anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
874255,166,1249,83,90,1,35,6,So bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatī’ ti. 
874256,166,1249,91,95,1,36,4,Yena cāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkama; 
874257,166,1249,96,115,1,69,8,upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandāhi[ vandāhi evañca vadehi( sabbattha) aññasuttesu pana natthi]–
874258,166,1249,116,125,1,59,6,"‘ anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
874259,166,1249,126,134,1,47,7,So āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandatī’ ti. 
874260,166,1249,135,137,1,13,2,Evañca vadehi–
874261,166,1249,138,157,1,115,13,"‘ sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’’ ti."
874262,166,1250,2,19,1,95,13,"‘ ‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho so puriso anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
874263,166,1250,20,25,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
874264,166,1250,26,33,1,53,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
874265,166,1250,34,44,1,59,6,"‘‘ anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
874266,166,1250,45,53,1,35,6,So bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatī’’ ti. 
874267,166,1250,54,58,1,36,4,Yena cāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; 
874268,166,1250,59,65,1,64,6,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
874269,166,1250,66,75,1,63,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca–
874270,166,1250,76,86,1,59,6,"‘‘ anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
874271,166,1250,87,93,1,44,6,So āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandati; 
874272,166,1250,94,96,1,13,2,evañca vadeti–
874273,166,1250,97,118,1,115,13,"‘ sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’’ ti. "
874274,166,1250,119,124,1,44,5,Adhivāsesi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhībhāvena. 
874275,166,1251,2,20,1,144,14,384. Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya āyasmatā ānandena pacchāsamaṇena yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; 
874276,166,1251,21,26,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
