875169,166,1374,2,33,1,156,19,"425.‘‘ Cakkhuñca, bhikkhave, paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā. "
875170,166,1374,34,43,1,76,9,So sukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno abhinandati abhivadati ajjhosāya tiṭṭhati. 
875171,166,1374,44,47,1,24,3,Tassa rāgānusayo anuseti. 
875172,166,1374,48,60,1,95,11,Dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno socati kilamati paridevati urattāḷiṃ kandati sammohaṃ āpajjati. 
875173,166,1374,61,64,1,27,3,Tassa paṭighānusayo anuseti. 
875174,166,1374,65,78,1,139,13,Adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno tassā vedanāya samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. 
875175,166,1374,79,82,1,26,3,Tassa avijjānusayo anuseti. 
875176,166,1374,83,112,1,260,26,"So vata, bhikkhave, sukhāya vedanāya rāgānusayaṃ appahāya dukkhāya vedanāya paṭighānusayaṃ appaṭivinodetvā adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya avijjānusayaṃ asamūhanitvā avijjaṃ appahāya vijjaṃ anuppādetvā diṭṭheva dhamme dukkhassantakaro bhavissatīti– netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
875177,166,1375,2,75,1,407,52,"‘ ‘ Sotañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca sadde ca uppajjati sotaviññāṇaṃ… pe… ghānañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca gandhe ca uppajjati ghānaviññāṇaṃ… pe… jivhañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca rase ca uppajjati jivhāviññāṇaṃ… pe… kāyañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca phoṭṭhabbe ca uppajjati kāyaviññāṇaṃ… pe… manañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca dhamme ca uppajjati manoviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā. "
875178,166,1375,76,85,1,76,9,So sukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno abhinandati abhivadati ajjhosāya tiṭṭhati. 
875179,166,1375,86,89,1,24,3,Tassa rāgānusayo anuseti. 
875180,166,1375,90,102,1,95,11,Dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno socati kilamati paridevati urattāḷiṃ kandati sammohaṃ āpajjati. 
