875183,166,1375,121,124,1,26,3,Tassa avijjānusayo anuseti. 
875184,166,1375,125,154,1,260,26,"So vata, bhikkhave, sukhāya vedanāya rāgānusayaṃ appahāya dukkhāya vedanāya paṭighānusayaṃ appaṭivinodetvā adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya avijjānusayaṃ asamūhanitvā avijjaṃ appahāya vijjaṃ anuppādetvā diṭṭheva dhamme dukkhassantakaro bhavissatīti– netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
875185,166,1376,2,32,1,156,19,"426.‘‘ Cakkhuñca , bhikkhave, paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā. "
875186,166,1376,33,42,1,79,9,So sukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno nābhinandati nābhivadati nājjhosāya tiṭṭhati. 
875187,166,1376,43,46,1,25,3,Tassa rāgānusayo nānuseti. 
875188,166,1376,47,63,1,107,15,Dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno na socati na kilamati paridevati na urattāḷiṃ kandati na sammohaṃ āpajjati. 
875189,166,1376,64,67,1,28,3,Tassa paṭighānusayo nānuseti. 
875190,166,1376,68,82,1,136,13,Adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno tassā vedanāya samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. 
875191,166,1376,83,86,1,27,3,Tassa avijjānusayo nānuseti. 
875192,166,1376,87,116,1,249,25,"So vata, bhikkhave, sukhāya vedanāya rāgānusayaṃ pahāya dukkhāya vedanāya paṭighānusayaṃ paṭivinodetvā adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya avijjānusayaṃ samūhanitvā avijjaṃ pahāya vijjaṃ uppādetvā diṭṭheva dhamme dukkhassantakaro bhavissatīti– ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
875193,166,1377,2,16,1,60,9,"‘ ‘ Sotañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca sadde ca uppajjati sotaviññāṇaṃ… pe…."
875194,166,1378,2,16,1,63,9,"‘ ‘ Ghānañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca gandhe ca uppajjati ghānaviññāṇaṃ… pe…."
875195,166,1379,2,17,1,61,9,"‘ ‘ Jivhañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca rase ca uppajjati jivhāviññāṇaṃ… pe… ."
875196,166,1380,2,16,1,65,9,"‘ ‘ Kāyañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca phoṭṭhabbe ca uppajjati kāyaviññāṇaṃ… pe…."
875197,166,1381,2,26,1,154,20,"‘ ‘ Manañca, bhikkhave, paṭicca dhamme ca uppajjati manoviññāṇaṃ tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā. "
875198,166,1381,27,36,1,79,9,So sukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno nābhinandati nābhivadati nājjhosāya tiṭṭhati. 
875199,166,1381,37,40,1,25,3,Tassa rāgānusayo nānuseti. 
875200,166,1381,41,57,1,110,16,Dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno na socati na kilamati na paridevati na urattāḷiṃ kandati na sammohaṃ āpajjati. 
875201,166,1381,58,61,1,28,3,Tassa paṭighānusayo nānuseti. 
875202,166,1381,62,75,1,136,13,Adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno tassā vedanāya samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. 
875203,166,1381,76,79,1,27,3,Tassa avijjānusayo nānuseti. 
875204,166,1381,80,108,1,249,25,"So vata, bhikkhave, sukhāya vedanāya rāgānusayaṃ pahāya dukkhāya vedanāya paṭighānusayaṃ paṭivinodetvā adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya avijjānusayaṃ samūhanitvā avijjaṃ pahāya vijjaṃ uppādetvā diṭṭheva dhamme dukkhassantakaro bhavissatīti– ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. "
875205,166,1382,2,43,1,171,17,"427.‘‘ Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmiṃ[ cakkhusmimpi( syā. kaṃ.) evamitaresupi] nibbindati, rūpesu nibbindati, cakkhuviññāṇe nibbindati, cakkhusamphasse nibbindati, vedanāya nibbindati, taṇhāya nibbindati. "
875206,166,1382,44,88,1,290,29,"Sotasmiṃ nibbindati, saddesu nibbindati… pe… ghānasmiṃ nibbindati, gandhesu nibbindati… jivhāya nibbindati, rasesu nibbindati… kāyasmiṃ nibbindati, phoṭṭhabbesu nibbindati… manasmiṃ nibbindati, dhammesu nibbindati, manoviññāṇe nibbindati, manosamphasse nibbindati, vedanāya nibbindati, taṇhāya nibbindati. "
875207,166,1382,89,95,1,36,4,"Nibbindaṃ virajjati , virāgā vimuccati. "
875208,166,1382,96,101,1,34,4,Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti.
875209,166,1382,102,120,1,82,11,"‘ Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ ti pajānātī’’ ti. "
875210,166,1383,2,4,1,17,2,Idamavoca bhagavā. 
