875214,166,1385,2,4,1,22,2,7 . Mahāsaḷāyatanikasuttaṃ 
875215,166,1386,2,20,1,87,11,428. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
875216,166,1386,21,26,1,34,5,Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi–
875217,166,1386,27,33,1,12,2,‘‘ bhikkhavo’’ ti.
875218,166,1386,34,44,1,44,6,‘‘ Bhadante’’ ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. 
