875300,166,1411,2,4,1,20,2,8 . Nagaravindeyyasuttaṃ 
875301,166,1412,2,28,1,152,19,434. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena nagaravindaṃ nāma kosalānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ gāmo tadavasari. 
875302,166,1412,29,40,1,47,4,Assosuṃ kho nagaravindeyyakā[ nagaravindeyyā( ka.)] brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
875303,166,1412,41,61,1,134,15,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ nagaravindaṃ anuppatto. "
875304,166,1412,62,71,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
875305,166,1412,72,89,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
875306,166,1412,90,104,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
875307,166,1412,105,118,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
875308,166,1412,119,129,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
875309,166,1413,2,9,1,74,7,Atha kho nagaravindeyyakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
875310,166,1413,10,16,1,67,6,upasaṅkamitvā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
875311,166,1413,17,21,1,38,4,Appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu; 
875312,166,1413,22,28,1,61,6,sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
875313,166,1413,29,36,1,63,7,Appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
875314,166,1413,37,44,1,66,7,Appekacce bhagavato santike nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
875315,166,1413,45,49,1,40,4,Appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
875316,166,1413,50,58,1,75,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho nagaravindeyyake brāhmaṇagahapatike bhagavā etadavoca– 
875317,166,1414,2,17,1,59,7,"435.‘‘ Sace vo, gahapatayo, aññatitthiyā paribbājakā evaṃ puccheyyuṃ–"
875318,166,1414,18,34,1,95,12,"‘ kathaṃbhūtā, gahapatayo, samaṇabrāhmaṇā na sakkātabbā na garukātabbā na mānetabbā na pūjetabbā’ ti? "
875319,166,1414,35,46,1,84,9,"Evaṃ puṭṭhā tumhe, gahapatayo, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ evaṃ byākareyyātha–"
875320,166,1414,47,76,1,219,25,"‘ ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu avītarāgā avītadosā avītamohā, ajjhattaṃ avūpasantacittā, samavisamaṃ caranti kāyena vācāya manasā, evarūpā samaṇabrāhmaṇā na sakkātabbā na garukātabbā na mānetabbā na pūjetabbā. "
875321,166,1414,77,80,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
875322,166,1414,81,105,1,176,20,"Mayampi hi cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu avītarāgā avītadosā avītamohā, ajjhattaṃ avūpasantacittā, samavisamaṃ carāma kāyena vācāya manasā, tesaṃ no samacariyampi hetaṃ uttari apassataṃ. "
875323,166,1414,106,118,1,85,12,Tasmā te bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā na sakkātabbā na garukātabbā na mānetabbā na pūjetabbā. 
875324,166,1414,119,159,1,318,33,"Ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā sotaviññeyyesu saddesu… ghānaviññeyyesu gandhesu… jivhāviññeyyesu rasesu… kāyaviññeyyesu phoṭṭhabbesu… manoviññeyyesu dhammesu avītarāgā avītadosā avītamohā, ajjhattaṃ avūpasantacittā, samavisamaṃ caranti kāyena vācāya manasā, evarūpā samaṇabrāhmaṇā na sakkātabbā na garukātabbā na mānetabbā na pūjetabbā. "
