875367,166,1421,64,85,1,46,5,"Mahāpurisavihāro eso[ hesa( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)], sāriputta, yadidaṃ– suññatā. "
875368,166,1421,86,93,1,43,5,"Tasmātiha, sāriputta, bhikkhu sace ākaṅkheyya–"
