875461,166,1439,2,53,1,67,9,"453. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā gajaṅgalāyaṃ[ kajaṅgalāyaṃ( sī. pī.), kajjaṅgalāyaṃ( syā. kaṃ.)] viharati suveḷuvane[ veḷuvane( syā. kaṃ.), mukheluvane( sī. pī.)]. "
875462,166,1439,54,80,1,67,8,"Atha kho uttaro māṇavo pārāsiviyantevāsī[ pārāsariyantevāsī( sī. pī.), pārāsiriyantevāsī( syā. kaṃ.)] yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
875463,166,1439,81,85,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
875464,166,1439,86,92,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
875465,166,1439,93,101,1,75,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho uttaraṃ māṇavaṃ pārāsiviyantevāsiṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
875466,166,1439,102,115,1,62,7,"‘‘ deseti, uttara, pārāsiviyo brāhmaṇo sāvakānaṃ indriyabhāvanan’’ ti?"
875467,166,1439,116,130,1,66,8,"‘‘ Deseti, bho gotama, pārāsiviyo brāhmaṇo sāvakānaṃ indriyabhāvanan’’ ti."
875468,166,1439,131,147,1,80,10,"‘‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, uttara, deseti pārāsiviyo brāhmaṇo sāvakānaṃ indriyabhāvanan’’ ti?"
875469,166,1439,148,179,1,141,21,"‘‘ Idha, bho gotama, cakkhunā rūpaṃ na passati, sotena saddaṃ na suṇāti– evaṃ kho, bho gotama, deseti pārāsiviyo brāhmaṇo sāvakānaṃ indriyabhāvanan’’ ti."
875470,166,1439,180,195,1,85,10,"‘‘ Evaṃ sante kho, uttara, andho bhāvitindriyo bhavissati, badhiro bhāvitindriyo bhavissati; "
875471,166,1439,196,200,1,39,4,yathā pārāsiviyassa brāhmaṇassa vacanaṃ. 
875472,166,1439,201,219,1,76,13,"Andho hi, uttara, cakkhunā rūpaṃ na passati, badhiro sotena saddaṃ na suṇātī’’ ti. "
875473,166,1439,220,233,1,119,12,"Evaṃ vutte, uttaro māṇavo pārāsiviyantevāsī tuṇhībhūto maṅkubhūto pattakkhandho adhomukho pajjhāyanto appaṭibhāno nisīdi. "
875474,166,1440,2,19,1,163,16,Atha kho bhagavā uttaraṃ māṇavaṃ pārāsiviyantevāsiṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ maṅkubhūtaṃ pattakkhandhaṃ adhomukhaṃ pajjhāyantaṃ appaṭibhānaṃ viditvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi–
875475,166,1440,20,45,1,140,17,"‘‘ aññathā kho, ānanda, deseti pārāsiviyo brāhmaṇo sāvakānaṃ indriyabhāvanaṃ, aññathā ca panānanda, ariyassa vinaye anuttarā indriyabhāvanā hotī’’ ti."
