875522,166,1445,30,43,1,69,9,"‘ uppannaṃ kho me idaṃ manāpaṃ, uppannaṃ amanāpaṃ, uppannaṃ manāpāmanāpaṃ. "
875523,166,1445,44,49,1,47,5,Tañca kho saṅkhataṃ oḷārikaṃ paṭiccasamuppannaṃ. 
875524,166,1445,50,59,1,43,7,Etaṃ santaṃ etaṃ paṇītaṃ yadidaṃ– upekkhā’ ti. 
