875769,167,152,2,16,1,63,9,20. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati tapodārāme. 
875770,167,152,17,29,1,106,12,Atha kho āyasmā samiddhi rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ paccuṭṭhāya yena tapodā tenupasaṅkami gattāni parisiñcituṃ. 
875771,167,152,30,38,1,81,8,Tapode gattāni parisiñcitvā paccuttaritvā ekacīvaro aṭṭhāsi gattāni pubbāpayamāno. 
875772,167,152,39,53,1,127,14,Atha kho aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ tapodaṃ obhāsetvā yena āyasmā samiddhi tenupasaṅkami; 
875773,167,152,54,61,1,67,7,upasaṅkamitvā vehāsaṃ ṭhitā āyasmantaṃ samiddhiṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi–
