875777,167,156,2,13,1,47,8,"Tasmā abhutvā bhikkhāmi, mā maṃ kālo upaccagā’’ ti. "
875778,167,157,2,24,1,74,9,Atha kho sā devatā pathaviyaṃ[ paṭhaviyaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] patiṭṭhahitvā āyasmantaṃ samiddhiṃ etadavoca–
