876194,167,485,2,12,1,58,9,Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi–
876195,167,486,2,12,1,54,8,"‘ ‘ Chetvā khīlaṃ chetvā palighaṃ, indakhīlaṃ ūhacca manejā; "
876196,167,487,2,13,1,55,8,"Te caranti suddhā vimalā, cakkhumatā sudantā susunāgā’’ ti. "
876197,167,488,2,11,1,58,9,Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi–
876198,167,489,2,14,1,59,10,"‘ ‘ Ye keci buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gatāse, na te gamissanti apāyabhūmiṃ; "
876199,167,490,2,11,1,48,6,"Pahāya mānusaṃ dehaṃ, devakāyaṃ paripūressantī’’ ti."
876200,167,491,2,4,1,14,2,8 . Sakalikasuttaṃ 
876201,167,492,2,18,1,77,10,38. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati maddakucchismiṃ migadāye. 
876202,167,492,19,35,1,59,9,Tena kho pana samayena bhagavato pādo sakalikāya[ sakkhalikāya( ka.)] khato hoti. 
876203,167,492,36,62,1,93,13,Bhusā sudaṃ bhagavato vedanā vattanti sārīrikā vedanā dukkhā tibbā[ tippā( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] kharā kaṭukā asātā amanāpā; 
876204,167,492,63,71,1,55,7,tā sudaṃ bhagavā sato sampajāno adhivāseti avihaññamāno. 
876205,167,492,72,87,1,122,15,Atha kho bhagavā catugguṇaṃ saṅghāṭiṃ paññāpetvā dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ kappeti pāde pādaṃ accādhāya sato sampajāno. 
876206,167,493,2,17,1,146,14,Atha kho sattasatā satullapakāyikā devatāyo abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ maddakucchiṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
876207,167,493,18,23,1,56,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. 
876208,167,493,24,34,1,68,10,Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
876209,167,493,35,45,1,27,5,"‘‘ nāgo vata, bho, samaṇo gotamo; "
876210,167,493,46,64,1,120,16,nāgavatā ca samuppannā sārīrikā vedanā dukkhā tibbā kharā kaṭukā asātā amanāpā sato sampajāno adhivāseti avihaññamāno’’ ti. 
876211,167,494,2,11,1,59,9,Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
876212,167,494,12,21,1,27,5,"‘‘ sīho vata, bho, samaṇo gotamo; "
876213,167,494,22,40,1,120,16,sīhavatā ca samuppannā sārīrikā vedanā dukkhā tibbā kharā kaṭukā asātā amanāpā sato sampajāno adhivāseti avihaññamāno’’ ti. 
876214,167,495,2,12,1,59,9,Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
