876226,167,499,2,11,1,59,9,Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
876227,167,499,12,48,1,108,12,"‘‘ passa samādhiṃ subhāvitaṃ cittañca suvimuttaṃ, na cābhinataṃ na cāpanataṃ na ca sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagataṃ[ sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritavataṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.), sasaṅkhāraniggayhavārivāvataṃ( ka.)]. "
876228,167,499,49,65,1,141,13,Yo evarūpaṃ purisanāgaṃ purisasīhaṃ purisaājānīyaṃ purisanisabhaṃ purisadhorayhaṃ purisadantaṃ atikkamitabbaṃ maññeyya kimaññatra adassanā’’ ti.
876229,167,500,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Pañcavedā sataṃ samaṃ, tapassī brāhmaṇā caraṃ; "
876230,167,501,2,12,1,61,9,"Cittañca nesaṃ na sammā vimuttaṃ, hīnattharūpā na pāraṅgamā te."
876231,167,502,2,11,1,60,7,"‘ ‘ Taṇhādhipannā vatasīlabaddhā, lūkhaṃ tapaṃ vassasataṃ carantā; "
876232,167,503,2,12,1,61,9,"Cittañca nesaṃ na sammā vimuttaṃ, hīnattharūpā na pāraṅgamā te."
876233,167,504,2,12,1,55,8,"‘ ‘ Na mānakāmassa damo idhatthi, na monamatthi asamāhitassa; "
876234,167,505,2,14,1,61,9,"Eko araññe viharaṃ pamatto, na maccudheyyassa tareyya pāran’’ ti."
