876236,167,507,2,13,1,65,8,"Eko araññe viharamappamatto, sa maccudheyyassa tareyya pāra’’ ntntti."
876237,167,508,2,4,1,26,2,9 . Paṭhamapajjunnadhītusuttaṃ 
876238,167,509,2,18,1,78,10,39. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ. 
876239,167,509,19,33,1,132,14,Atha kho kokanadā pajjunnassa dhītā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ mahāvanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
876240,167,509,34,39,1,55,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
876241,167,509,40,53,1,93,13,Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā kokanadā pajjunnassa dhītā bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi–
