876245,167,513,2,10,1,50,7,"Sāhaṃ dāni sakkhi jānāmi, munino desayato sugatassa."
876246,167,514,2,12,1,51,8,"‘ ‘ Ye keci ariyaṃ dhammaṃ, vigarahantā caranti dummedhā; "
876247,167,515,2,9,1,52,6,"Upenti roruvaṃ ghoraṃ, cirarattaṃ dukkhaṃ anubhavanti."
876248,167,516,2,13,1,47,9,"‘ ‘ Ye ca kho ariye dhamme, khantiyā upasamena upetā; "
876249,167,517,2,11,1,47,6,"Pahāya mānusaṃ dehaṃ, devakāya paripūressantī’’ ti."
