876635,167,896,2,22,1,87,11,82. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
876636,167,896,23,36,1,123,13,Atha kho kassapo devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
876637,167,896,37,42,1,55,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
876638,167,896,43,50,1,59,7,Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho kassapo devaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
876639,167,896,51,64,1,53,8,"‘‘ bhikkhuṃ bhagavā pakāsesi, no ca bhikkhuno anusāsan’’ ti."
876640,167,896,65,76,1,40,6,"‘‘ Tena hi kassapa, taññevettha paṭibhātū’’ ti."
876641,167,897,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Subhāsitassa sikkhetha, samaṇūpāsanassa ca; "
876642,167,898,2,11,1,41,6,"Ekāsanassa ca raho, cittavūpasamassa cā’’ ti. "
876643,167,899,2,5,1,27,3,Idamavoca kassapo devaputto; 
876644,167,899,6,9,1,22,3,samanuñño satthā ahosi. 
876645,167,899,10,27,1,112,13,Atha kho kassapo devaputto‘‘ samanuñño me satthā’’ ti bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti.
