876724,167,964,30,40,1,73,10,Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho tāyano devaputto bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi–
876725,167,965,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Chinda sotaṃ parakkamma, kāme panuda brāhmaṇa; "
876726,167,966,2,7,1,38,4,"Nappahāya munī kāme, nekattamupapajjati."
