876893,167,1101,2,4,1,19,2,10 . Anāthapiṇḍikasuttaṃ 
876894,167,1102,2,16,1,80,10,101. Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi–
876895,167,1103,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ, isisaṅghanisevitaṃ; "
876896,167,1104,2,7,1,41,4,"Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena, pītisañjananaṃ mama."
876897,167,1105,2,13,1,46,8,"‘ ‘ Kammaṃ vijjā ca dhammo ca, sīlaṃ jīvitamuttamaṃ; "
876898,167,1106,2,10,1,43,7,"Etena maccā sujjhanti, na gottena dhanena vā."
876899,167,1107,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Tasmā hi paṇḍito poso, sampassaṃ atthamattano; "
876900,167,1108,2,11,1,44,6,"Yoniso vicine dhammaṃ, evaṃ tattha visujjhati."
876901,167,1109,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Sāriputtova paññāya, sīlena upasamena ca; "
876902,167,1110,2,11,1,42,6,"Yopi pāraṅgato bhikkhu, etāvaparamo siyā’’ ti. "
876903,167,1111,2,5,1,33,3,Idamavoca anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto. 
876904,167,1111,6,13,1,73,7,Idaṃ vatvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti. 
876905,167,1112,2,11,1,56,8,Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi–
876906,167,1112,12,29,1,132,13,"‘‘ imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññataro devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
876907,167,1112,30,35,1,47,5,upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
876908,167,1112,36,49,1,74,11,"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho, bhikkhave, so devaputto mama santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi–"
876909,167,1113,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Idañhi taṃ jetavanaṃ, isisaṅghanisevitaṃ; "
876910,167,1114,2,7,1,41,4,"Āvutthaṃ dhammarājena, pītisañjananaṃ mama."
