876918,167,1121,11,21,1,66,8,Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyī’’ ti. 
876919,167,1122,2,10,1,46,6,"Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
876920,167,1122,11,22,1,52,7,"‘‘ so hi nūna, bhante, anāthapiṇḍiko devaputto bhavissati. "
876921,167,1122,23,32,1,64,7,Anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati āyasmante sāriputte abhippasanno ahosī’’ ti.
