877038,167,1186,2,12,1,46,8,"‘ ‘ Ke ca te ataruṃ paṅkaṃ, maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ; "
877039,167,1187,2,12,1,46,7,"Ke hitvā mānusaṃ dehaṃ, dibbayogaṃ upaccagun’’ ti."
877040,167,1188,2,19,1,39,8,"‘ ‘ Upako palagaṇḍo[ phalagaṇḍo( ka.)] ca, pukkusāti ca te tayo; "
877041,167,1189,2,20,1,43,6,"Bhaddiyo khaṇḍadevo ca, bāhuraggi ca saṅgiyo[ bāhudantī ca piṅgiyo( sī. syā.)]; "
