877045,167,1193,2,12,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Na aññatra bhagavatā, nāññatra tava sāsanā; "
877046,167,1194,2,8,1,46,5,"Yassa te dhammamaññāya, acchiduṃ bhavabandhanaṃ."
877047,167,1195,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Yattha nāmañca rūpañca, asesaṃ uparujjhati; "
877048,167,1196,2,12,1,51,7,"Taṃ te dhammaṃ idhaññāya, acchiduṃ bhavabandhanan’’ ti."
