877064,167,1212,2,4,1,11,2,5 . Jantusuttaṃ 
877065,167,1213,2,31,1,198,21,"106. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ sambahulā bhikkhū, kosalesu viharanti himavantapasse araññakuṭikāya uddhatā unnaḷā capalā mukharā vikiṇṇavācā muṭṭhassatino asampajānā asamāhitā vibbhantacittā pākatindriyā. "
877066,167,1214,2,13,1,78,10,Atha kho jantu devaputto tadahuposathe pannarase yena te bhikkhū tenupasaṅkami; 
877067,167,1214,14,19,1,43,5,upasaṅkamitvā te bhikkhū gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi–
877068,167,1215,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Sukhajīvino pure āsuṃ, bhikkhū gotamasāvakā; "
877069,167,1216,2,13,1,39,4,"Anicchā piṇḍamesanā[ piṇḍamesānā(?)], anicchā sayanāsanaṃ; "
877070,167,1217,2,9,1,44,6,"Loke aniccataṃ ñatvā, dukkhassantaṃ akaṃsu te."
877071,167,1218,2,11,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Dupposaṃ katvā attānaṃ, gāme gāmaṇikā viya; "
877072,167,1219,2,8,1,44,5,"Bhutvā bhutvā nipajjanti, parāgāresu mucchitā."
877073,167,1220,2,17,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Saṅghassa añjaliṃ katvā, idhekacce vadāmahaṃ[ vandāmahaṃ( ka.)]; "
877074,167,1221,2,18,1,41,7,"Apaviddhā anāthā te, yathā petā tatheva te[ tatheva ca( sī.)]."
