877078,167,1225,2,7,1,15,1,107. Sāvatthinidānaṃ. 
877079,167,1225,8,15,1,61,7,Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho rohitasso devaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
877080,167,1225,16,70,1,155,29,"‘‘ yattha nu kho, bhante, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati[ na jiyyati na miyyati( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] na cavati na upapajjati, sakkā nu kho so, bhante, gamanena lokassa anto ñātuṃ vā daṭṭhuṃ vā pāpuṇituṃ vā’’ ti?"
877081,167,1225,71,102,1,145,23,"‘‘ Yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī’’ ti."
