877085,167,1227,2,15,1,77,10,"‘ ‘ Bhūtapubbāhaṃ, bhante, rohitasso nāma isi ahosiṃ bhojaputto iddhimā vehāsaṅgamo. "
877086,167,1227,16,25,1,38,6,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpo javo ahosi; "
