877088,167,1227,52,60,1,46,6,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpo padavītihāro ahosi; "
877089,167,1227,61,67,1,51,6,seyyathāpi nāma puratthimā samuddā pacchimo samuddo. 
877090,167,1227,68,76,1,47,6,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpaṃ icchāgataṃ uppajji–"
877091,167,1227,77,85,1,42,6,‘ ahaṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ pāpuṇissāmī’ ti. 
877092,167,1227,86,112,1,258,24,"So khvāhaṃ, bhante, evarūpena javena samannāgato evarūpena ca padavītihārena aññatreva asita-pīta-khāyita-sāyitā aññatra uccāra-passāvakammā aññatra niddākilamathapaṭivinodanā vassasatāyuko vassasatajīvī vassasataṃ gantvā appatvāva lokassa antaṃ antarāva kālaṅkato."
