877189,167,1269,2,42,1,47,7,"Appiccho sorato danto, kālaṃ kaṅkhati sudanto’’[ kālaṃ kaṅkhati bhatako sudanto( sī.), kālaṃ kaṅkhati bhāvito sudanto( syā. kaṃ.), kālaṃ kaṅkhati bhatiko sudanto( pī.)] ti."
877190,167,1270,2,4,1,24,2,10 . Nānātitthiyasāvakasuttaṃ 
877191,167,1271,2,17,1,77,10,111. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. 
877192,167,1271,18,91,1,215,26,"Atha kho sambahulā nānātitthiyasāvakā devaputtā asamo ca sahali[ sahalī( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] ca nīko[ niṅko( sī. pī.), niko( syā. kaṃ.)] ca ākoṭako ca vegabbhari ca[ veṭambarī ca( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] māṇavagāmiyo ca abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ veḷuvanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; "
