877861,167,1562,35,45,1,54,6,"‘‘ cattārome, mahārāja, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
877862,167,1562,46,48,1,14,2,Katame cattāro? 
877863,167,1562,49,58,1,67,4,"Tamotamaparāyano, tamojotiparāyano, jotitamaparāyano, jotijotiparāyano’’."
877864,167,1563,2,10,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, mahārāja puggalo tamotamaparāyano hoti? "
877865,167,1563,11,54,1,204,25,"Idha, mahārāja, ekacco puggalo nīce kule paccājāto hoti, caṇḍālakule vā venakule[ veṇakule( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] vā nesādakule vā rathakārakule vā pukkusakule vā dalidde appannapānabhojane kasiravuttike , yattha kasirena ghāsacchādo labbhati. "
877866,167,1563,55,86,1,180,23,"So ca hoti dubbaṇṇo duddasiko okoṭimako bavhābādho[ bahvābādho( ka.)] kāṇo vā kuṇī vā khañjo vā pakkhahato vā, na lābhī annassa pānassa vatthassa yānassa mālāgandhavilepanassa seyyāvasathapadīpeyyassa. "
877867,167,1563,87,99,1,77,10,"So kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati. "
877868,167,1563,100,120,1,152,19,"So kāyena duccaritaṃ caritvā vācāya duccaritaṃ caritvā manasā duccaritaṃ caritvā, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
877869,167,1564,2,24,1,120,16,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja , puriso andhakārā vā andhakāraṃ gaccheyya, tamā vā tamaṃ gaccheyya, lohitamalā vā lohitamalaṃ gaccheyya. "
877870,167,1564,25,32,1,42,5,"Tathūpamāhaṃ, mahārāja, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
877871,167,1564,33,41,1,47,6,"Evaṃ kho, mahārāja, puggalo tamotamaparāyano hoti."
877872,167,1565,2,11,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, mahārāja, puggalo tamojotiparāyano hoti? "
877873,167,1565,12,41,1,204,25,"Idha, mahārāja, ekacco puggalo nīce kule paccājāto hoti, caṇḍālakule vā venakule vā nesādakule vā rathakārakule vā pukkusakule vā dalidde appannapānabhojane kasiravuttike, yattha kasirena ghāsacchādo labbhati. "
877874,167,1565,42,70,1,184,24,"So ca kho hoti dubbaṇṇo duddasiko okoṭimako bavhābādho, kāṇo vā kuṇī vā khañjo vā pakkhahato vā, na lābhī annassa pānassa vatthassa yānassa mālāgandhavilepanassa seyyāvasathapadīpeyyassa. "
877875,167,1565,71,83,1,74,10,"So kāyena sucaritaṃ carati, vācāya sucaritaṃ carati, manasā sucaritaṃ carati. "
877876,167,1565,84,103,1,136,18,"So kāyena sucaritaṃ caritvā vācāya sucaritaṃ caritvā manasā sucaritaṃ caritvā, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati."
877877,167,1566,2,28,1,167,20,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, mahārāja, puriso pathaviyā vā pallaṅkaṃ āroheyya, pallaṅkā vā assapiṭṭhiṃ āroheyya, assapiṭṭhiyā vā hatthikkhandhaṃ āroheyya, hatthikkhandhā vā pāsādaṃ āroheyya. "
877878,167,1566,29,36,1,42,5,"Tathūpamāhaṃ, mahārāja, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
877879,167,1566,37,45,1,47,6,"Evaṃ kho, mahārāja, puggalo tamojotiparāyano hoti."
877880,167,1567,2,11,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, mahārāja, puggalo jotitamaparāyano hoti? "
877881,167,1567,12,38,1,211,20,"Idha , mahārāja, ekacco puggalo ucce kule paccājāto hoti, khattiyamahāsālakule vā brāhmaṇamahāsālakule vā gahapatimahāsālakule vā, aḍḍhe mahaddhane mahābhoge pahūtajātarūparajate pahūtavittūpakaraṇe pahūtadhanadhaññe. "
877882,167,1567,39,57,1,164,16,"So ca hoti abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko, paramāya vaṇṇapokkharatāya samannāgato, lābhī annassa pānassa vatthassa yānassa mālāgandhavilepanassa seyyāvasathapadīpeyyassa. "
877883,167,1567,58,70,1,77,10,"So kāyena duccaritaṃ carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati. "
877884,167,1567,71,91,1,152,19,"So kāyena duccaritaṃ caritvā vācāya duccaritaṃ caritvā manasā duccaritaṃ caritvā, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati."
