877977,167,1613,130,142,1,103,11,Atha āgaccheyya khattiyakumāro asikkhito akatahattho akatayoggo akatūpāsano bhīru chambhī utrāsī palāyī. 
877978,167,1613,143,155,1,55,9,"Bhareyyāsi taṃ purisaṃ, attho ca te tādisena purisenā’’ ti?"
877979,167,1613,156,175,1,70,12,"‘‘ Nāhaṃ, bhante, bhareyyaṃ taṃ purisaṃ, na ca me attho tādisena purisenā’’ ti."
