877988,167,1615,2,43,1,157,21,"‘ ‘ Evameva kho, mahārāja, yasmā kasmā cepi[ yasmā cepi( sī. syā. kaṃ. ka.)] kulā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti, so ca hoti pañcaṅgavippahīno pañcaṅgasamannāgato, tasmiṃ dinnaṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti. "
