878020,167,1633,38,46,1,74,8,Tatthaddasaṃ mahantaṃ pabbataṃ abbhasamaṃ sabbe pāṇe nippothento āgacchati. 
878021,167,1633,47,58,1,39,7,"Yaṃ te, mahārāja, karaṇīyaṃ, taṃ karohī’ ti. "
878022,167,1633,59,85,1,170,22,Atha dutiyo puriso āgaccheyya pacchimāya disāya… pe… atha tatiyo puriso āgaccheyya uttarāya disāya… pe… atha catuttho puriso āgaccheyya dakkhiṇāya disāya saddhāyiko paccayiko. 
