878747,167,2033,2,13,1,43,9,"‘ ‘ Kiṃ nu jātiṃ na rocesi, jāto kāmāni bhuñjati; "
878748,167,2034,2,24,1,48,9,"Ko nu taṃ idamādapayi, jātiṃ mā roca[ mā rocesi( sī. pī.)] bhikkhunī’’ ti."
878749,167,2035,2,20,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Jātassa maraṇaṃ hoti, jāto dukkhāni phussati[ passati( sī. pī.)]; "
878750,167,2036,2,10,1,47,7,"Bandhaṃ vadhaṃ pariklesaṃ, tasmā jātiṃ na rocaye."
878751,167,2037,2,10,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Buddho dhammamadesesi, jātiyā samatikkamaṃ; "
878752,167,2038,2,8,1,42,5,"Sabbadukkhappahānāya , so maṃ sacce nivesayi."
878753,167,2039,2,14,1,40,8,"‘ ‘ Ye ca rūpūpagā sattā, ye ca arūpaṭṭhāyino; "
878754,167,2040,2,10,1,44,5,"Nirodhaṃ appajānantā, āgantāro punabbhavan’’ ti. "
878755,167,2041,2,18,1,85,12,Atha kho māro pāpimā‘‘ jānāti maṃ cālā bhikkhunī’’ ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti.
