878779,167,2056,45,58,1,42,7,"‘‘ kassa nu tvaṃ, bhikkhuni, pāsaṇḍaṃ rocesī’’ ti?"
878780,167,2056,59,72,1,43,7,"‘‘ Na khvāhaṃ, āvuso, kassaci pāsaṇḍaṃ rocemī’’ ti."
878781,167,2057,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Kaṃ nu uddissa muṇḍāsi, samaṇī viya dissasi; "
878782,167,2058,2,13,1,45,8,"Na ca rocesi pāsaṇḍaṃ, kimiva carasi momūhā’’ ti."
878783,167,2059,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Ito bahiddhā pāsaṇḍā, diṭṭhīsu pasīdanti te; "
878784,167,2060,2,10,1,44,7,"Na tesaṃ dhammaṃ rocemi, te dhammassa akovidā."
878785,167,2061,2,11,1,46,6,"‘ ‘ Atthtththi sakyakule jāto, buddho appaṭipuggalo; "
