878788,167,2064,2,7,1,46,4,"Sabbakammakkhayaṃ patto, vimutto upadhisaṅkhaye; "
878789,167,2065,2,13,1,48,8,"So mayhaṃ bhagavā satthā, tassa rocemi sāsanan’’ ti. "
878790,167,2066,2,18,1,91,12,Atha kho māro pāpimā‘‘ jānāti maṃ sīsupacālā bhikkhunī’’ ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti.
