878809,167,2079,2,4,1,12,2,10 . Vajirāsuttaṃ 
878810,167,2080,2,8,1,15,1,171. Sāvatthinidānaṃ . 
878811,167,2080,9,20,1,94,10,Atha kho vajirā bhikkhunī pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
878812,167,2080,21,31,1,104,9,Sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkantā yena andhavanaṃ tenupasaṅkami divāvihārāya. 
878813,167,2080,32,38,1,66,6,Andhavanaṃ ajjhogāhetvā aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle divāvihāraṃ nisīdi. 
878814,167,2080,39,55,1,144,16,Atha kho māro pāpimā vajirāya bhikkhuniyā bhayaṃ chambhitattaṃ lomahaṃsaṃ uppādetukāmo samādhimhā cāvetukāmo yena vajirā bhikkhunī tenupasaṅkami; 
878815,167,2080,56,61,1,51,5,upasaṅkamitvā vajiraṃ bhikkhuniṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi–
878816,167,2081,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Kenāyaṃ pakato satto, kuvaṃ sattassa kārako; "
878817,167,2082,2,12,1,48,7,"Kuvaṃ satto samuppanno, kuvaṃ satto nirujjhatī’’ ti. "
878818,167,2083,2,7,1,39,5,Atha kho vajirāya bhikkhuniyā etadahosi–
878819,167,2083,8,22,1,54,10,‘‘ ko nu khvāyaṃ manusso vā amanusso vā gāthaṃ bhāsatī’’ ti? 
