879009,167,2210,2,8,1,15,1,176. Sāvatthinidānaṃ . 
879010,167,2210,9,20,1,86,11,Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa brahmuno evarūpaṃ pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ uppannaṃ hoti–
