879012,167,2210,36,55,1,123,15,Atha kho bhagavā tassa brahmuno cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya– seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso… pe… tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. 
879013,167,2210,56,67,1,87,11,Atha kho bhagavā tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā. 
879014,167,2211,2,7,1,45,5,Atha kho āyasmato mahāmoggallānassa etadahosi–
879015,167,2211,8,19,1,40,7,‘‘ kahaṃ nu kho bhagavā etarahi viharatī’’ ti? 
879016,167,2211,20,44,1,163,17,Addasā kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno[ mahāmoggalāno( ka.)] bhagavantaṃ dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisinnaṃ tejodhātuṃ samāpannaṃ. 
879017,167,2211,45,67,1,154,19,"Disvāna– seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya evameva– jetavane antarahito tasmiṃ brahmaloke pāturahosi. "
879018,167,2211,68,93,1,147,17,Atha kho āyasmā mahāmoggallāno puratthimaṃ disaṃ nissāya[ upanissāya( sī.)] tassa brahmuno upari vehāsaṃ pallaṅkena nisīdi tejodhātuṃ samāpajjitvā nīcataraṃ bhagavato. 
