879365,167,2370,22,51,1,138,18,Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa dhanañjānī[ dhānañjānī( pī. sī. aṭṭha.)] nāma brāhmaṇī abhippasannā hoti buddhe ca dhamme ca saṅghe ca. 
879366,167,2370,52,64,1,120,12,Atha kho dhanañjānī brāhmaṇī bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa bhattaṃ upasaṃharantī upakkhalitvā tikkhattuṃ udānaṃ udānesi–
