879372,167,2374,26,38,1,54,8,"Idāni tyāhaṃ, vasali, tassa satthuno vādaṃ āropessāmī’’ ti."
879373,167,2374,39,63,1,168,19,"‘‘ Na khvāhaṃ taṃ, brāhmaṇa, passāmi sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya, yo tassa bhagavato vādaṃ āropeyya arahato sammāsambuddhassa. "
879374,167,2374,64,87,1,49,8,"Api ca tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, gaccha, gantvā vijānissasī’’ ti[ gantvāpi jānissasīti( syā. kaṃ.)]. "
