879605,167,2511,2,4,1,17,2,10 . Bahudhītarasuttaṃ 
879606,167,2512,2,13,1,61,7,196. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe. 
879607,167,2512,14,25,1,98,11,Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa catuddasa balībaddā naṭṭhā honti. 
879608,167,2512,26,37,1,88,11,Atha kho bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo te balībadde gavesanto yena so vanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkami; 
879609,167,2512,38,52,1,129,14,upasaṅkamitvā addasa bhagavantaṃ tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. 
