879641,167,2541,10,21,1,45,6,"‘‘ abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama! "
879642,167,2541,22,48,1,169,20,"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya– cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantīti; "
879643,167,2541,49,55,1,54,6,evameva bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. 
879644,167,2541,56,63,1,68,7,Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. 
