879710,167,2583,2,4,1,14,2,3 . Devahitasuttaṃ 
879711,167,2584,2,8,1,15,1,199. Sāvatthinidānaṃ . 
879712,167,2584,9,16,1,49,7,Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā vātehābādhiko hoti; 
879713,167,2584,17,23,1,42,6,āyasmā ca upavāṇo bhagavato upaṭṭhāko hoti. 
879714,167,2584,24,30,1,45,6,Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ āmantesi–
879715,167,2584,31,44,1,41,7,"‘‘ iṅgha me tvaṃ, upavāṇa, uṇhodakaṃ jānāhī’’ ti."
879716,167,2584,45,65,1,135,15,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’ ti kho āyasmā upavāṇo bhagavato paṭissutvā nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena devahitassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
879717,167,2584,66,70,1,42,4,upasaṅkamitvā tuṇhībhūto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. 
879718,167,2584,71,81,1,77,9,Addasā kho devahito brāhmaṇo āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ. 
