879742,167,2600,2,4,1,14,2,4 . Mahāsālasuttaṃ 
879743,167,2601,2,8,1,15,1,200. Sāvatthinidānaṃ . 
879744,167,2601,9,32,1,81,9,Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇamahāsālo lūkho lūkhapāvuraṇo [ lūkhapāpuraṇo( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
879745,167,2601,33,37,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
879746,167,2601,38,44,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
879747,167,2601,45,53,1,62,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho taṃ brāhmaṇamahāsālaṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
879748,167,2601,54,66,1,42,6,"‘‘ kinnu tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, lūkho lūkhapāvuraṇo’’ ti?"
879749,167,2601,67,77,1,32,6,"‘‘ Idha me, bho gotama, cattāro puttā. "
879750,167,2601,78,87,1,44,7,Te maṃ dārehi saṃpuccha gharā nikkhāmentī’’ ti.
879751,167,2601,88,106,1,114,14,"‘‘ Tena hi tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imā gāthāyo pariyāpuṇitvā sabhāyaṃ mahājanakāye sannipatite puttesu ca sannisinnesu bhāsassu–"
879752,167,2602,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Yehi jātehi nandissaṃ, yesañca bhavamicchisaṃ; "
879753,167,2603,2,10,1,44,7,"Te maṃ dārehi saṃpuccha, sāva vārenti sūkaraṃ."
879754,167,2604,2,12,1,41,8,"‘ ‘ Asantā kira maṃ jammā, tāta tātāti bhāsare; "
879755,167,2605,2,8,1,41,5,"Rakkhasā puttarūpena, te jahanti vayogataṃ."
879756,167,2606,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Assova jiṇṇo nibbhogo, khādanā apanīyati; "
879757,167,2607,2,8,1,41,5,"Bālakānaṃ pitā thero, parāgāresu bhikkhati."
879758,167,2608,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Daṇḍova kira me seyyo, yañce puttā anassavā; "
879759,167,2609,2,9,1,44,6,"Caṇḍampi goṇaṃ vāreti, atho caṇḍampi kukkuraṃ."
879760,167,2610,2,11,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Andhakāre pure hoti, gambhīre gādhamedhati; "
879761,167,2611,2,10,1,44,5,"Daṇḍassa ānubhāvena, khalitvā patitiṭṭhatī’’ ti. "
879762,167,2612,2,18,1,137,16,Atha kho so brāhmaṇamahāsālo bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo pariyāpuṇitvā sabhāyaṃ mahājanakāye sannipatite puttesu ca sannisinnesu abhāsi–
879763,167,2613,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Yehi jātehi nandissaṃ, yesañca bhavamicchisaṃ; "
879764,167,2614,2,11,1,44,7,"Te maṃ dārehi saṃpuccha, sāva vārenti sūkaraṃ."
879765,167,2615,2,12,1,41,8,"‘ ‘ Asantā kira maṃ jammā, tāta tātāti bhāsare; "
879766,167,2616,2,8,1,41,5,"Rakkhasā puttarūpena, te jahanti vayogataṃ."
