879773,167,2623,2,14,1,90,11,Atha kho naṃ brāhmaṇamahāsālaṃ puttā gharaṃ netvā nhāpetvā paccekaṃ dussayugena acchādesuṃ. 
879774,167,2623,15,25,1,77,10,Atha kho so brāhmaṇamahāsālo ekaṃ dussayugaṃ ādāya yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
879775,167,2623,26,30,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
879776,167,2623,31,37,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
879777,167,2623,38,44,1,60,6,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho brāhmaṇamahāsālo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
879778,167,2623,45,57,1,66,8,"‘‘ mayaṃ, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā nāma ācariyassa ācariyadhanaṃ pariyesāma. "
879779,167,2623,58,66,1,46,6,Paṭiggaṇhatu me bhavaṃ gotamo ācariyadhanan’’ ti. 
