879857,167,2656,2,4,1,16,2,8 . Kaṭṭhahārasuttaṃ 
879858,167,2657,2,13,1,61,7,204. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe. 
879859,167,2657,14,29,1,140,14,Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa sambahulā antevāsikā kaṭṭhahārakā māṇavakā yena vanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
879860,167,2657,30,44,1,132,14,upasaṅkamitvā addasaṃsu bhagavantaṃ tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. 
879861,167,2657,45,50,1,54,5,Disvāna yena bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
879862,167,2657,51,55,1,51,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhāradvājagottaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavocuṃ–
879863,167,2657,56,62,1,23,3,"‘‘ yagghe, bhavaṃ jāneyyāsi! "
879864,167,2657,63,77,1,105,12,Asukasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe samaṇo nisinno pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā’’. 
879865,167,2657,78,89,1,89,11,Atha kho bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo tehi māṇavakehi saddhiṃ yena so vanasaṇḍo tenupasaṅkami. 
879866,167,2657,90,104,1,119,14,Addasā kho bhagavantaṃ tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā. 
