879869,167,2658,2,7,1,29,4,"‘ ‘ Gambhīrarūpe bahubherave vane, "
879870,167,2659,2,6,1,31,4,Suññaṃ araññaṃ vijanaṃ vigāhiya; 
879871,167,2660,2,6,1,28,3,"Aniñjamānena ṭhitena vaggunā, "
879872,167,2661,2,6,1,32,4,Sucārurūpaṃ vata bhikkhu jhāyasi.
