879876,167,2665,2,6,1,27,4,Yadekako pītimano vane vase.
879877,167,2666,2,7,1,32,3,"‘ ‘ Maññāmahaṃ lokādhipatisahabyataṃ, "
879878,167,2667,2,5,1,29,3,Ākaṅkhamāno tidivaṃ anuttaraṃ; 
879879,167,2668,2,6,1,33,3,"Kasmā bhavaṃ vijanamaraññamassito, "
