879910,167,2686,21,27,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
879911,167,2686,28,35,1,62,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho bhikkhako brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
879912,167,2686,36,56,1,77,12,"‘‘ ahampi kho, bho gotama, bhikkhako, bhavampi bhikkhako, idha no kiṃ nānākaraṇan’’ ti?"
879913,167,2687,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Na tena bhikkhako hoti, yāvatā bhikkhate pare; "
879914,167,2688,2,10,1,46,7,"Vissaṃ dhammaṃ samādāya, bhikkhu hoti na tāvatā."
879915,167,2689,2,11,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Yodha puññañca pāpañca, bāhitvā brahmacariyaṃ; "
879916,167,2690,2,13,1,47,8,"Saṅkhāya loke carati, sa ve bhikkhūti vuccatī’’ ti. "
879917,167,2691,2,9,1,51,6,"Evaṃ vutte, bhikkhako brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
879918,167,2691,10,36,1,120,17,"‘‘ abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama… pe… upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan’’ ti."
879919,167,2692,2,4,1,15,2,11 . Saṅgāravasuttaṃ 
879920,167,2693,2,7,1,15,1,207. Sāvatthinidānaṃ. 
879921,167,2693,8,27,1,159,17,"Tena kho pana samayena saṅgāravo nāma brāhmaṇo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati udakasuddhiko, udakena parisuddhiṃ pacceti, sāyaṃ pātaṃ udakorohanānuyogamanuyutto viharati. "
879922,167,2693,28,39,1,91,10,Atha kho āyasmā ānando pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya sāvatthiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
879923,167,2693,40,48,1,88,8,Sāvatthiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
879924,167,2693,49,54,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
879925,167,2693,55,63,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
879926,167,2693,64,86,1,144,15,"‘‘ idha, bhante, saṅgāravo nāma brāhmaṇo sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasati udakasuddhiko , udakena suddhiṃ pacceti, sāyaṃ pātaṃ udakorohanānuyogamanuyutto viharati. "
879927,167,2693,87,102,1,97,11,"Sādhu, bhante, bhagavā yena saṅgāravassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’’ ti. "
879928,167,2693,103,106,1,31,3,Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. 
879929,167,2694,2,14,1,114,11,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena saṅgāravassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami ; 
879930,167,2694,15,19,1,35,4,upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. 
879931,167,2694,20,27,1,54,7,Atha kho saṅgāravo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
879932,167,2694,28,32,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
879933,167,2694,33,39,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
879934,167,2694,40,47,1,61,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho saṅgāravaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
879935,167,2694,48,69,1,114,13,"‘‘ saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, udakasuddhiko, udakena suddhiṃ paccesi, sāyaṃ pātaṃ udakorohanānuyogamanuyutto viharasī’’ ti?"
879936,167,2694,70,78,1,15,3,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho gotama’’."
879937,167,2694,79,101,1,132,14,"‘‘ Kiṃ pana tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno udakasuddhiko, udakasuddhiṃ paccesi, sāyaṃ pātaṃ udakorohanānuyogamanuyutto viharasī’’ ti?"
879938,167,2694,102,156,1,136,22,"‘‘ Idha me, bho gotama[ idha me bho gotama ahaṃ( pī. ka.)], yaṃ divā pāpakammaṃ kataṃ hoti, taṃ sāyaṃ nhānena[ nahānena( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] pavāhemi, yaṃ rattiṃ pāpakammaṃ kataṃ hoti taṃ pātaṃ nhānena pavāhemi. "
879939,167,2694,157,178,1,136,15,"Imaṃ khvāhaṃ, bho gotama, atthavasaṃ sampassamāno udakasuddhiko, udakena suddhiṃ paccemi, sāyaṃ pātaṃ udakorohanānuyogamanuyutto viharāmī’’ ti."
879940,167,2695,2,8,1,33,5,"‘ ‘ Dhammo rahado brāhmaṇa sīlatittho, "
879941,167,2696,2,6,1,29,4,Anāvilo sabbhi sataṃ pasattho; 
879942,167,2697,2,6,1,27,4,"Yattha have vedaguno sinātā, "
879943,167,2698,2,15,1,30,4,Anallagattāva [ anallīnagattāva( ka.)] taranti pāran’’ ti. 
879944,167,2699,2,9,1,51,6,"Evaṃ vutte, saṅgāravo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–"
