879946,167,2700,2,4,1,16,2,12 . Khomadussasuttaṃ 
879947,167,2701,2,22,1,85,12,208. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati khomadussaṃ nāmaṃ sakyānaṃ nigamo. 
879948,167,2701,23,34,1,95,10,Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya khomadussaṃ nigamaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. 
879949,167,2701,35,51,1,130,15,"Tena kho pana samayena khomadussakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā sabhāyaṃ sannipatitā honti kenacideva karaṇīyena, devo ca ekamekaṃ phusāyati. "
879950,167,2701,52,59,1,44,7,Atha kho bhagavā yena sā sabhā tenupasaṅkami. 
879951,167,2701,60,66,1,74,6,Addasaṃsu khomadussakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā bhagavantaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. 
879952,167,2701,67,69,1,18,2,Disvāna etadavocuṃ–
879953,167,2701,70,84,1,55,9,"‘‘ ke ca muṇḍakā samaṇakā, ke ca sabhādhammaṃ jānissantī’’ ti? "
879954,167,2701,85,92,1,67,7,Atha kho bhagavā khomadussake brāhmaṇagahapatike gāthāya ajjhabhāsi–
879955,167,2702,2,10,1,32,7,"‘ ‘ Nesā sabhā yattha na santi santo, "
879956,167,2703,2,9,1,33,7,Santo na te ye na vadanti dhammaṃ; 
879957,167,2704,2,6,1,28,4,"Rāgañca dosañca pahāya mohaṃ, "
879958,167,2705,2,10,1,36,6,Dhammaṃ vadantā ca bhavanti santo’’ ti. 
879959,167,2706,2,9,1,65,6,"Evaṃ vutte, khomadussakā brāhmaṇagahapatikā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ–"
879960,167,2706,10,21,1,45,6,"‘‘ abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama; "
879961,167,2706,22,56,1,225,26,"seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya– cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantīti, evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. "
879962,167,2706,57,65,1,71,8,Ete mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāma dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. 
879963,167,2706,66,78,1,67,10,Upāsake no bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupete saraṇaṃ gate’’ ti. 
879964,167,2707,2,4,1,19,2,Upāsakavaggo dutiyo. 
879965,167,2708,2,3,1,11,1,Tassuddānaṃ – 
879966,167,2709,2,7,1,37,4,"Kasi udayo devahito, aññataramahāsālaṃ; "
879967,167,2710,2,6,1,46,3,"Mānathaddhaṃ paccanīkaṃ, navakammikakaṭṭhahāraṃ; "
879968,167,2711,2,9,1,57,6,"Mātuposakaṃ bhikkhako, saṅgāravo ca khomadussena dvādasāti. "
879969,167,2712,2,4,1,26,2,Brāhmaṇasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. 
879970,167,2713,1,4,1,16,1,8. Vaṅgīsasaṃyuttaṃ
879971,167,2714,2,4,1,15,2,1 . Nikkhantasuttaṃ 
879972,167,2715,2,26,1,120,15,209. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā vaṅgīso āḷaviyaṃ viharati aggāḷave cetiye āyasmatā nigrodhakappena upajjhāyena saddhiṃ. 
879973,167,2715,27,38,1,84,11,Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā vaṅgīso navako hoti acirapabbajito ohiyyako vihārapālo. 
879974,167,2715,39,49,1,97,10,Atha kho sambahulā itthiyo samalaṅkaritvā yena aggāḷavako ārāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃsu vihārapekkhikāyo. 
879975,167,2715,50,63,1,91,12,"Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa tā itthiyo disvā anabhirati uppajjati, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti. "
879976,167,2715,64,69,1,38,5,Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi–
879977,167,2715,70,80,1,31,7,"‘‘ alābhā vata me, na vata me lābhā; "
879978,167,2715,81,89,1,39,7,"dulladdhaṃ vata me, na vata me suladdhaṃ; "
879979,167,2715,90,110,1,126,17,"yassa me anabhirati uppannā, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti, taṃ kutettha labbhā, yaṃ me paro anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyya. "
879980,167,2715,111,121,1,72,8,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ attanāva attano anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyyan’’ ti. 
879981,167,2715,122,137,1,114,15,Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso attanāva attano anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādetvā tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imā gāthāyo abhāsi–
879982,167,2716,2,10,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Nikkhantaṃ vata maṃ santaṃ, agārasmānagāriyaṃ; "
879983,167,2717,2,8,1,40,5,"Vitakkā upadhāvanti, pagabbhā kaṇhato ime."
879984,167,2718,2,10,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Uggaputtā mahissāsā, sikkhitā daḷhadhammino; "
879985,167,2719,2,7,1,40,4,"Samantā parikireyyuṃ, sahassaṃ apalāyinaṃ."
879986,167,2720,2,29,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Sacepi etato[ ettato( sī. pī. ka.), ettakā( syā. kaṃ.)] bhiyyo, āgamissanti itthiyo; "
879987,167,2721,2,15,1,48,6,"Neva maṃ byādhayissanti[ byāthayissanti(?)], dhamme samhi patiṭṭhitaṃ."
879988,167,2722,2,13,1,46,7,"‘ ‘ Sakkhī hi me sutaṃ etaṃ, buddhassādiccabandhuno; "
879989,167,2723,2,9,1,43,6,"Nibbānagamanaṃ maggaṃ, tattha me nirato mano."
879990,167,2724,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Evañce maṃ viharantaṃ, pāpima upagacchasi; "
879991,167,2725,2,13,1,48,8,"Tathā maccu karissāmi, na me maggampi dakkhasī’’ ti."
879992,167,2726,2,4,1,11,2,2 . Aratisuttaṃ 
879993,167,2727,2,22,1,109,13,210. Ekaṃ samayaṃ… pe… āyasmā vaṅgīso āḷaviyaṃ viharati aggāḷave cetiye āyasmatā nigrodhakappena upajjhāyena saddhiṃ. 
879994,167,2727,23,40,1,131,16,"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā nigrodhakappo pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto vihāraṃ pavisati, sāyaṃ vā nikkhamati aparajju vā kāle. "
879995,167,2727,41,54,1,91,12,"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmato vaṅgīsassa anabhirati uppannā hoti, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti. "
879996,167,2727,55,60,1,38,5,Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi–
879997,167,2727,61,71,1,31,7,"‘‘ alābhā vata me, na vata me lābhā; "
879998,167,2727,72,80,1,39,7,"dulladdhaṃ vata me, na vata me suladdhaṃ; "
879999,167,2727,81,89,1,52,7,"yassa me anabhirati uppannā, rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃseti; "
880000,167,2727,90,101,1,73,10,"taṃ kutettha labbhā, yaṃ me paro anabhiratiṃ vinodetvā abhiratiṃ uppādeyya. "
